NK120(e)002:1: // sdom pa gsum gyi dris lan nyi 'od snang ba zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK120(e)002:3: dgongs don dang po ltar na spyir rgyal ba'i bstan
NK120(e)002:4: pa ni rjod byed lung dang brjod bya rtogs pa
NK120(e)002:5: gnyis dang / de la'ang rgyu lam du byed pa
NK120(e)002:6: mdo dang 'bras bu lam du byed pa sngags kyi
NK120(e)002:7: gnyis dang / theg pa gnyis / de'ang gnas skabs drang don dang mthar thug nges don gnyis dang /
NK120(e)002:8: de'ang zab mo lta ba'i cha dang rgya chen spyod
NK120(e)002:9: pa'i cha gnyis re dbyer yod cing 'jig rten mthun
NK120(e)002:10: 'jug gi tshul gyi lha mi'i theg pa rnams dang
NK120(e)002:11: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa rnams la drang
NK120(e)002:12: don dgongs pa can sogs kun kyang dngos dang brgyud
NK120(e)002:13: pa'i sgo nas mthar thug sangs rgyas 'thob pa'i rgyur
NK120(e)002:14: mi 'gro ba med pas gnas skabs so so'i gdul
NK120(e)002:15: bya rang rang gi ngor bden zhing gtso che la
NK120(e)002:16: / khyad par du brjod bya rtogs pa'i chos rnams
NK120(e)002:17: sdom pa gsum du bsdus nas nyams su len pas
NK120(e)002:18: bstan pa kun gyi gnad bslab pa gsum la tshang
NK120(e)002:19: dgos pas sdom pa gsum po'ang gtso che chung 'dra
NK120(e)002:20: / ste / rjod byed kyi theg pa la rgyu
NK120(e)002:21: 'bras gnyis su nges pa ltar brjod bya sdom pa
NK120(e)002:22: gsum la'ang snga ma snga ma rgyud dang phyi ma
NK120(e)002:23: phyi ma 'bras bu snga ma yan lag dang phyi
NK120(e)002:24: ma nying lag gam rten dang brten pa sogs kyi
NK120(e)002:26: bstan pa go rim dang bstun na'ang 'dul ba ni
NK120(e)002:27: 'khor lo dang po'i brjod bya bden pa bzhi dang
NK120(e)002:28: lhag pa'i tshul khrims kyi bslab pa yin pas de
NK120(e)002:31: ji ltar 'di na shing rtsa gtso bo ste //
NK120(e)002:32: rnam par 'phel dang kun 'dzin gnyis kyi gzhi /
NK120(e)002:33: de bzhin dam chos tshogs rnams kun gyi yang //
NK120(e)002:34: gzhi dang rtsa ba 'dul ba yin par bshad //
NK120(e)002:35: ces bstan pa kun gyi rtsa bar gsungs shing /
NK120(e)002:37: gang na las yod cing de la nan tan byed
NK120(e)002:38: pa de na bstan pa yod cing gang na las
NK120(e)002:39: med cing de la nan tan mi byed pa de
NK120(e)002:40: na bstan pa med ces gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:41: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i rten gyi dbang du byed na'ang spyod 'jug las /
NK120(e)002:42: bstan rtsa dge slong nyid yin na //
NK120(e)002:43: zhes pa don dam pa'i dge slong yang yin mod so sor thar pa'i dge slong yang yin te /
NK120(e)002:45: thub bstan rin chen sgron me mchog /'bar ba'i snod du dka' thub can //
NK120(e)002:47: dge slong rnams ni yin phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:49: gang na 'dul ba 'dzin pa yod pa de na
NK120(e)002:50: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las chung ba yin no
NK120(e)002:52: gang zag gi blo rigs kyi bstan pa la 'jug rim gyi dbang du byed na /
NK120(e)002:53: lam mas sbyangs dang las dang po pa rnams la
NK120(e)002:54: ni 'khor lo dang po'i dgongs don spyod pa spong
NK120(e)002:55: bdun gyi tshul khrims dang sgom pa bden bzhi'i blang
NK120(e)002:56: dor dang lta ba gang zag gi bdag med pa
NK120(e)002:57: tsam de gtso che ste blo dman 'jug bde zhing
NK120(e)002:58: lam gong ma'i sgo'am drang byed yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:60: sems rta kha blan dka' ba la //
NK120(e)002:61: mthun pa'i gzir rnon brgya ba yi //
NK120(e)002:62: srab ni so sor thar 'di yin //
NK120(e)002:63: zhes gang zag gi rgyud 'dul ba'i thabs dang po yin par gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:64: de ltar na so thar dang de'i sdom pa ni
NK120(e)002:65: rtsa ba'am gzhi yin la byang sems dang de'i sdom
NK120(e)002:66: pa ni grogs sam thabs yin la /
NK120(e)002:67: rdo rje'i theg pa dang de'i sdom pa ni snying
NK120(e)002:68: po'am 'bras bu yin pas mthar thug theg pa gcig
NK120(e)002:69: pu rdo rje'i theg pa'i lam 'bras mthar thug 'grub
NK120(e)002:70: pa la ni don gyi gnad thams cad dngos dang
NK120(e)002:72: gnas skabs kyi theg pa rang rang la ltos nas
NK120(e)002:73: nyan rang lta bu'i gang zag gi rang lam gyi
NK120(e)002:74: 'bras bu nyi tshe ba 'thob pa la ni lam
NK120(e)002:75: gong ma gnyis kyi bslab bya thun mong ma yin
NK120(e)002:76: pa rnams mi dgos par rang lam nor 'khrul med
NK120(e)002:77: pa des chog / byang chub sems dpa'i 'bras bu
NK120(e)002:78: 'bring 'thob pa la sngags kyi lta sgom spyod pa
NK120(e)002:79: thun min de mi dgos par sems bskyed sogs rang
NK120(e)002:80: lam gnad ma 'chug pa de nyid kyis chog mod
NK120(e)002:81: pa des chog / / 'og ma nyan thos kyi
NK120(e)002:82: spyod pa 'dul ba'i bslab bya rnams kyang dngos sam
NK120(e)002:83: brgyud nas nyams su blang dgos /
NK120(e)002:84: rig pa 'dzin pa'i lam 'bras mthar thug 'thob pa
NK120(e)002:85: la ni 'og ma gnyis kyang zhar la thob pa'am
NK120(e)002:86: sdom gsum rim gyis nod de dngos su tshang bar
NK120(e)002:87: bsgrub dgos so // 'on kyang sbyangs pa sngon song
NK120(e)002:88: dang lam thod rgal ba'i gang zag dbang rnon yin
NK120(e)002:89: na smin grol zab mo'i lam gong ma la bsnyegs
NK120(e)002:90: te de tshul bzhin shes pas gtso bor gzung na
NK120(e)002:91: 'og ma'i spang blang gis gnad thams cad zhor la
NK120(e)002:92: rdzogs pa yin pas lam 'og ma sngon du 'gro
NK120(e)002:94: dge bsnyen dang dge tshul gyi sdom pa sngon du
NK120(e)002:95: ma song bar thal byung du bsnyen rdzogs blangs na
NK120(e)002:96: thob par bshad pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:97: gzhan drangs pa sogs kyi dgos pa yod na 'og
NK120(e)002:98: ma'ang blangs te phyi'i kun spyod so thar ltar byed
NK120(e)002:99: dgos pa sogs ni dmigs bsal yin no //
NK120(e)002:100: mdor na las dang po pa blo dman rnams la
NK120(e)002:101: sor sdom gtso che ste rang rgyud sbyangs pa 'di
NK120(e)002:102: dang po chos la 'jug pa'i gzhi yin pa'i phyir
NK120(e)002:103: / dper na byang sems las dang po pas kyang
NK120(e)002:104: dang po nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims gtso bor
NK120(e)002:105: / srung ba dang / rig pa 'dzin pa dang
NK120(e)002:106: po'i las can rnams kyang dang po spyi'i dam tshig
NK120(e)002:107: brtul zhugs nyer lnga sogs nyes spyod sdom pa gtso
NK120(e)002:108: bor srung bar byed dgos pa bzhin te 'dul sdom
NK120(e)002:109: ji bzhin thub na byang sdom sla zhing /
NK120(e)002:110: byang sdom bslab gsum bsrungs na sngags la 'jug sla
NK120(e)002:111: zhing dam tshig thub cing tshegs chung ngus tshogs rdzogs
NK120(e)002:112: par 'gyur ro // blo na 'phar ba'i dbang 'bring
NK120(e)002:113: gzhan don nus pa'i theg chen rigs can rnams la
NK120(e)002:115: mdo lam yun ring pa'i sgrub mi nus pa'am sngags
NK120(e)002:116: la mos pa che zhing sgrub nus pa'i gang zag
NK120(e)002:117: shin tu blo chen las 'phro can rnams la sngags
NK120(e)002:119: dbang rnon gyis tshe 'dir 'grub pa'i nye lam dang
NK120(e)002:120: don gnyis rlabs chen 'grub pa'i thabs shes khyad par
NK120(e)002:121: can gyi chos yin pa'i phyir dper na in+d+ra b+hu
NK120(e)002:123: gsang sngags tshul chen shin tu rmad byung ba //
NK120(e)002:124: lam gyi nang nas nye lam chen po dang //
NK120(e)002:125: thabs kyi nang nas ma nor dam pa ste //
NK120(e)002:126: shes rab nang nas shes rab khyad par can //
NK120(e)002:128: rtogs bya de kho na nyid dang thob bya sangs rgyas /
NK120(e)002:129: 'thob byed byang chub kyi sems sogs mdo sngags gnyis don gcig kyang /
NK120(e)002:130: de dag rgyud la myur du skye ba'i thabs ma
NK120(e)002:131: rmongs pa dang thabs mang ba dang dka' ba med
NK120(e)002:132: pa dang / dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK120(e)002:133: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK120(e)002:134: zhes 'phags chos bzhi tshul gsum pa'i sgron me sogs las mang du gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:135: rang nyid la mchog gi nye lam sgrub pa'i nus
NK120(e)002:136: pa yod bzhin de dor nas dman lam sgrub pa
NK120(e)002:137: don med de rtsa ltung chen po 'byung ba dang
NK120(e)002:138: rigs nyams pa dang zab mo'i skal ba 'chad pa'i
NK120(e)002:139: phyir / nus pa med cing mos pa zhan na 'og ma nas slob dgos pa sogs so //
NK120(e)002:140: des na bka' thams cad kyang gang zag gi blo'i
NK120(e)002:141: bye brag las ris tha dad pa du mar gyur
NK120(e)002:142: pa yin te / dgongs pa lung ston las /
NK120(e)002:143: rtog pa med cing 'khrug med pa //
NK120(e)002:144: yid 'ong rdo rje'i gsung gcig pu //
NK120(e)002:145: gdul bya so so'i dbang gis ni //
NK120(e)002:146: bye brag mang por gyur pa yin //
NK120(e)002:148: de ltar 'khor lo gsum po'i spyod pa'i cha rnams
NK120(e)002:149: kyi 'jug rim dang gtso phal rnams gdul bya'i blo
NK120(e)002:150: dang bstun dgos pa bzhin lta ba'i cha rnams kyang
NK120(e)002:151: las dang po pa'i gang zag rnams la 'khor lo
NK120(e)002:152: dang po'i bstan don 'dus byas mi rtag pa dang
NK120(e)002:153: / gang zag gi bdag med pa dang bdag des phung po stong pa tsam gtso che zhing /
NK120(e)002:154: de nas blo cung zad smin pa la chos thams
NK120(e)002:155: cad bdag gnyis kyis stong pa nyid 'khor lo bar
NK120(e)002:156: pa'i bstan don mtha' bzhi bral ba'i lta ba dang
NK120(e)002:157: / de nas blo shin tu smin pa'i gang zag
NK120(e)002:158: la tha ma'i bstan don rig stong bde bar gshegs
NK120(e)002:159: pa'i snying po dang sngags kyi dbang bzhi pa'i lta
NK120(e)002:160: ba 'od gsal ba'i ye shes bde stong lhan cig
NK120(e)002:161: skyes pa'i don dam gtso che ste nges don mthar
NK120(e)002:163: de yang smin byed kyi dbang dang dam tshig dang
NK120(e)002:164: grol byed kyi lam rim pa gnyis kyi thabs la
NK120(e)002:165: mkhas na 'di'i lta ba stong pa nyid dang rang
NK120(e)002:166: byung gi ye shes zung du 'jug pa de nyid
NK120(e)002:168: spros pa thams cad 'gog pa dbu ma'i lta ba
NK120(e)002:169: zab cing bzang mod mdo lam yin pas ji ltar
NK120(e)002:170: myur kyang grangs med gsum du tshogs gnyis ma bsags
NK120(e)002:171: par lta ba de mthar phyin par rtogs mi nus
NK120(e)002:173: ji srid dge ba'i rtsa ba de ni ma rdzogs par //
NK120(e)002:174: de srid stong nyid dam pa de ni rtogs mi byed //
NK120(e)002:176: 'khor lo dang po gnyis kyi bdag med dang stong
NK120(e)002:177: nyid bcu drug sogs kyang phyi mar 'du zhing rnam
NK120(e)002:178: grangs pa'i don dam de dag kyang rnam grangs min
NK120(e)002:179: pa'i don dam tha ma'i brjod bya mthar thug khas
NK120(e)002:180: len kun bral 'od gsal ba'i ye shes nyid du
NK120(e)002:182: des na 'khor lo bar tha'i stong rkyang dang snying
NK120(e)002:183: po bstan pa gnyis kyang gdul bya'i blo'i rtag chad
NK120(e)002:184: bzlog cing dgos dbang tsam las gnyis ka gnad gcig
NK120(e)002:185: tu 'bab ste / bar ba'i dus su phyi ma'i
NK120(e)002:186: snying po dang ye shes sogs kyang gab cing stong
NK120(e)002:188: phyi ma'i dus snying po 'od gsal rtsal du bton
NK120(e)002:189: nas gsungs pas bar ba'i dus su'ang ye shes kyi
NK120(e)002:190: snang cha tha snyad du'ang med pa ma yin zhing
NK120(e)002:191: / phyi ma snying po ston pa na'ang gzhi stong
NK120(e)002:192: pa chen po las ma 'das par rig pa'i ye
NK120(e)002:193: shes bden stong nyid rtsal du bton nas bstan pa
NK120(e)002:194: shes dgos pa sogs bka' dang dgongs 'grel thams cad
NK120(e)002:195: drang nges sogs zhib par ma phyes na rtag chad
NK120(e)002:196: du lhung ba dang spang blang gi nyes par 'gyur
NK120(e)002:197: / ba yin no // yang sdom pa gsum po
NK120(e)002:198: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la ji ltar gnas zhes
NK120(e)002:199: / ba yin no // gsungs pa la / so
NK120(e)002:200: so'i dbang du ni bshad ma thag pa ltar dang
NK120(e)002:201: / ba yin no // gsungs pa la / /
NK120(e)002:202: sdom pa gsum rim gyis nod pa'i gsum ldan rdo
NK120(e)002:203: rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud gcig la gsum po thob la
NK120(e)002:204: ma nyams par ldan tshul la bzhed tshul mang po
NK120(e)002:205: rgya bod gnyis kar byung yang rnying ma sogs phal
NK120(e)002:206: ches ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du
NK120(e)002:207: gnas par 'dod pa 'di shes na bade'am snyam pas
NK120(e)002:208: / ba yin no // gsungs pa la / /
NK120(e)002:209: / 'bum lnga'i lung las rdo yi rigs kyi sogs
NK120(e)002:210: lcags zangs dngul gsum la 'gyur rtsis btab pas thams
NK120(e)002:211: cad gser gyi ngo bo gcig tu gnas 'gyur yang
NK120(e)002:212: gsum po'i rin thang sogs kyi ldog pa tsam tha
NK120(e)002:213: dad du ming gi dbyer med pa ltar sdom pa
NK120(e)002:214: gsum kyang ngo bo shes par 'dod dgos pas don
NK120(e)002:215: gsum po de'i ngo bo 'dzin pa ni gtso sems
NK120(e)002:216: yid shes kho na yin pas ngo bo la gzhi
NK120(e)002:218: ldog pa la gzhi mthun mi srid pas gsum po'i
NK120(e)002:219: skabs so sor len yul cho ga dus tshod phan
NK120(e)002:220: yon nyams na gsor yod med sogs kyi ldog pa
NK120(e)002:221: tha dad du yod pas gsum ldan shi ba'i tshe
NK120(e)002:222: dang gtong rgyu byung ba'i tshe yang sor sdom gyi
NK120(e)002:224: gsum ldan gyis mi bsad pa la yan lag bzhi
NK120(e)002:225: tshang na nyams pa'i cha nas gsum ka nyams kyang
NK120(e)002:226: gtong ba'i cha nas srog gcod spong ba'i sdom pa
NK120(e)002:227: de gtong yang thams cad gtong ba min te /
NK120(e)002:228: yan lag gzhan la gtong rgyu ma byung zhing ltung
NK120(e)002:229: ba gcig byung bas thams cad cig car gtong na
NK120(e)002:230: sdom pa gcig blangs pas thams cad cig car thob
NK120(e)002:232: des na gtso sems yid shes gcig gi 'khor du
NK120(e)002:233: don gsum po'i khyad par 'dzin pa'i sems byung rigs
NK120(e)002:234: mi gcig pa'i ldog pa gsum rim can du 'byung
NK120(e)002:236: nges 'byung gi bsam pas zin pa'i gzhan gnod gzhi
NK120(e)002:237: bcas spong ba'i sor sdom gyi rigs can gyi sems
NK120(e)002:238: byung gcig dang / gzhan phan don du gnyer ba byang sdom gyi rigs can sems byung gcig dang /
NK120(e)002:239: snang srid dag mnyam chen po thabs shes khyad par
NK120(e)002:240: can sngags sdom gyi rigs can sems byung gcig ste
NK120(e)002:241: gsum gyi ldog pa dbyer rung ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:242: dper na bum pa'i lto ldir ba dang 'dus byas yin pa dang /
NK120(e)002:243: mi rtag pa yin pa gsum po bum pa tsam
NK120(e)002:244: du ngo bor gcig kyang ldog pa tha dad du
NK120(e)002:245: dbyer yod cing / gtso sems kyis bum pa'i ngo
NK120(e)002:246: bo tsam 'dzin sems byung gis don gyi khyad par
NK120(e)002:249: de la don mthong rnam par zhes //
NK120(e)002:250: de yi khyad par sems las byung //
NK120(e)002:252: spyir yang sdom pa gsum gyi ngo bo la ltos
NK120(e)002:253: nas sdom pa thob pa dang skye tshul sogs 'di
NK120(e)002:254: ltar lags te / dper na dkon mchog gsum la
NK120(e)002:255: yid ches kyi dad pa skyes na dge bsnyen gyi
NK120(e)002:257: ngan song gsum la skrag pas yid 'byung ste bslab
NK120(e)002:258: pa srung tshe sdom pa gnas pa dang chags pa
NK120(e)002:259: yin / spyir 'khor ba dang sgos gru de ji 'dra khyim de 'dra /
NK120(e)002:260: zhes pa'i khyim la dur khrod tsam du 'jigs tshe dge tshul gyi sdom pa skye nus yin /
NK120(e)002:261: khyim nas sbrul shubs 'don ltar byas nas 'dod yon
NK120(e)002:262: la zhen pa chung ba dang bslab pa mig 'bras
NK120(e)002:263: bzhin srung tshe sdom pa gnas shing chags pa yin
NK120(e)002:264: te / de ltar dge tshul gyur ma thag /'di la khyim pa thams cad kyis //
NK120(e)002:266: gang phyir khyim gyi 'ching grol phyir //
NK120(e)002:268: 'khor ba mtha' dag la snying po med cing me'i 'obs lta bur 'jigs shing /
NK120(e)002:269: dge tshul las kyang lhag par phyi 'dod yon dang
NK120(e)002:270: nang sems can la mi rtag sdug bsngal sogs shes
NK120(e)002:271: nas skyug bro ba byung tshe dge slong gi sdom
NK120(e)002:273: 'dod pa dang bral zhing thar lam la 'dun nas
NK120(e)002:274: g.yag rnga'i rtse mo bzhin du bslab pa srung tshe
NK120(e)002:275: sdom pa gnas shing chags pa yin te /
NK120(e)002:277: dge ba slong dang zas slong dang //
NK120(e)002:278: nye bar zhi dang chags bcom dang //
NK120(e)002:279: yid 'ong phyir na dge slong yin //
NK120(e)002:281: gzhan la snying rje lhag par skyes na byang sdom skye //
NK120(e)002:282: gzhan don du rdzogs byang don du gnyer nas smon
NK120(e)002:283: 'jug gi bslab pa srung tshe sdom pa gnas pa
NK120(e)002:285: de'ang dbang bskur thob nas tshe 'dir rdzogs byang thob par 'dod tshe sngags sdom skye /
NK120(e)002:286: sgo gsum rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs su mos pa
NK120(e)002:287: brtan nas dam tshig srog ltar srung tshe sngags sdom
NK120(e)002:288: gnas shing chags pa yin no //
NK120(e)002:289: de ltar ma yin par rang rang gi cho gas
NK120(e)002:290: rtags len pa dang bsrung bya khas blangs nas ci
NK120(e)002:291: mi snyam du 'dug pa la sdom pa mtshan nyid
NK120(e)002:292: pa yod par ma gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:293: so thar gyi sdom pa bye brag smra ba ltar
NK120(e)002:294: rnam rig min pa'i gzugs can bem por 'dod na
NK120(e)002:295: ni sdom pa'i ngo bo gnas 'gyur mi rung ste
NK120(e)002:296: bem po shes pa ru 'gyur mi srid pa'i phyir
NK120(e)002:297: dang / 'di'i sdom pa lus ngag las skye zhing
NK120(e)002:298: 'byung gyur gyi rdul dwangs ma zhig rten du 'dod
NK120(e)002:299: pas shi 'phos tshe 'byung bzhi'i phung po 'dor bas
NK120(e)002:300: kyang gtong ba'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK120(e)002:301: gnas 'gyur 'dod dgos te gsum po blangs pa bzhin
NK120(e)002:302: so sor ngo bo tha dad du 'dod na rdo
NK120(e)002:303: rje 'dzin pa yin na nyan thos kyi dge slong
NK120(e)002:304: yin pa dang / byang chub sems dpa' yin na
NK120(e)002:305: nyan thos yang yin dgos pa sogs kyi skyon du
NK120(e)002:306: 'gyur zhing byang sems rgyud ldan gyi gang zag la
NK120(e)002:307: rang don don gnyer gyi blo yod par thar bar
NK120(e)002:309: dper na lcags zangs dngul gsum la 'gyur rtsis btab
NK120(e)002:310: pas gser du bsgyur yang gsum po gnas ma gyur
NK120(e)002:311: par ngo bo tha dad du yod na gser yin
NK120(e)002:312: na lcags kyang yin dgos pa sogs kyi skyon 'bab
NK120(e)002:313: pa bzhin no // yang tshigs gsum rim can du
NK120(e)002:314: blangs pa'i dge slong gi rgyud la dge bsnyen dge
NK120(e)002:315: tshul gyi bslang ba'i ldog cha rnams thob la ma
NK120(e)002:316: nyams par yod kyang thams cad spong sems gcig gi
NK120(e)002:317: ngo bor gnas gyur cing yon tan yar ldan du
NK120(e)002:318: gyur zin pa'i phyir dge slong yin na dge bsnyen
NK120(e)002:319: kyang yin dgos pa dang ltung ba gcig byung na
NK120(e)002:320: nyes pa gsum cig char du skyed dgos pa sogs
NK120(e)002:321: kyi skyon med pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:322: spang blang nang mi 'gal bar nyams su len tshul gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:323: sdom pa gsum ga'i skabs su'ang rang gzhan la phan
NK120(e)002:324: par mi 'gyur zhing gnod pa'i cha rnams spang dgos
NK120(e)002:325: pa ni gnad gcig pa yin pas /
NK120(e)002:326: las dang po pa'i rab byung zhig gis dbang thob
NK120(e)002:327: pa tsam gyis 'og ma ltos med du btang nas
NK120(e)002:328: sngags spyod gtso bor byed pa sogs kyi rtsa ltung
NK120(e)002:329: 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pas mi rung ste bsrung bya
NK120(e)002:330: rnams gong mar 'du zhing kun slong dman pa sogs
NK120(e)002:331: kyi ldog pa re btang yon tan gyi cha gsar
NK120(e)002:332: ba re thob pa la spyi dbang thob pa tsam
NK120(e)002:333: gyis gnas 'gyur btags pa ba thob ces brjod kyang
NK120(e)002:334: / gnas 'gyur mtshan nyid pa ni dbang thob cing
NK120(e)002:335: dam tshig dang ldan pas rim gnyis bsgom pa las
NK120(e)002:336: byung ba'i gong ma'i lta ba mnyam pa chen po'i
NK120(e)002:337: don mthong ba la bya dgos pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:338: des na gang zag rang gi rgyud tshod dang sbyar
NK120(e)002:339: nas nyams su len dgos pa yin pas tshogs 'khor
NK120(e)002:340: gyi dus lta bur chang dang phyi dro'i kha zas
NK120(e)002:341: spyod dgos pa sogs bya ba mi 'dra ba gnyis
NK120(e)002:342: tho thug pa byung tshe brtags nas /
NK120(e)002:343: rtogs goms brtan cing don chen por 'gyur bar shes
NK120(e)002:344: na sngags gtso bor byas na 'og mar 'gal ba
NK120(e)002:345: ltar snang yang don la mi 'gal te /
NK120(e)002:346: ltung ba dngos gzhi skyed pa ni bdag 'dzin ma rig pa la rag las pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:347: chos rnams rmi lam lta bu mnyam pa nyid rtogs
NK120(e)002:348: pa la bcas ltung dngos gzhi mi bskyed pa mdo
NK120(e)002:349: las kyang / skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed cing //
NK120(e)002:350: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK120(e)002:352: rmi lam ni med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK120(e)002:353: las ni ma byas pa nyid do //
NK120(e)002:356: rgyud sde rnams las kyang mang du gsungs /
NK120(e)002:357: dper na bcas 'gal byung ba'i dgra bcom pa la ltung ba'i dngos gzhi mi 'jog pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:358: tho thug kyang sred pa rang mtshan pa dang rang
NK120(e)002:359: rgyud la skyon gyis gos par dogs pa dang bcas
NK120(e)002:360: shing don gzhan med par shes na ni 'og ma
NK120(e)002:361: gtso bor bya dgos te chos sngags yin kyang gang
NK120(e)002:362: zag sngags su ma song ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:363: sngags nus rgyud ldan can ni sngags kyi thabs shes gnyis ka khyad par can yin pas /
NK120(e)002:364: rma byas dug rjen par za ba lta bu'i gnad
NK120(e)002:365: la rtogs goms yod na 'og ma'i spang bya thams
NK120(e)002:366: cad gong ma'i lam du shar bas mi 'ching bar
NK120(e)002:367: ma zad yon tan skyed byed du'ang 'gro ste rma
NK120(e)002:368: bya'i mdangs dug gis 'phel ba bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:369: dper na 'o ma nyid mi la sman dang sbrul la dug tu 'gyur ba ltar /
NK120(e)002:370: rnam rtog gi rkyen gyis 'ching ba'i rgyur 'gyur gyi yul la 'ching ba'i dngos po ma grub bo //
NK120(e)002:373: yon tan lnga ldan rin chen nyid //
NK120(e)002:374: ma dag pas ni dug tu 'gyur //
NK120(e)002:375: dag pas bdud rtsir 'gyur ba yin //
NK120(e)002:377: skye bo mi bzad pa yi las //
NK120(e)002:379: thabs dang bcas na de nyid kyis //
NK120(e)002:382: de ltar min na dug rgyus yod pa'i phal pa
NK120(e)002:383: sogs kyis dug mi spyod pa'i thabs sogs kyis rang
NK120(e)002:384: la mi gnod par byed pa ltar nyan thos pas
NK120(e)002:385: spang bya'i gtso bo nyon mongs pa la dgra bzhin
NK120(e)002:386: bltas te thabs shes nyi tshe bas spang byar byas
NK120(e)002:387: na'ang rang rgyud mi 'ching zhing yon tan nyi tshe
NK120(e)002:388: ba skyed pa bzhin shes dgos so //
NK120(e)002:389: gcig la bkag pa kun la bkag pa dang gcig
NK120(e)002:390: zhugs pa'i lam la dang po nas kun 'jug dgos
NK120(e)002:391: pa min pas rang rgyud kyi khams dang nus pa
NK120(e)002:392: dang gzhan don 'gyur mi 'gyur sogs kyi gnad dang
NK120(e)002:393: bstun dgos pa'i dbye bsal shes dgos so //
NK120(e)002:394: nang thug pa lta bu'i rkyen med cing gzhan don
NK120(e)002:395: mi 'gyur ba dang rang rgyud ma smin par shes
NK120(e)002:396: na so sor rang lam ltar srung sdom dang gu
NK120(e)002:397: dogs bya dgos / rang rgyud smin cing gzhan don
NK120(e)002:398: 'gyur ba'i dgos pa sogs mthong na gong ma'i sbyor
NK120(e)002:399: sgrol gyi spyod pa barlanga po rnams kyang sgra ji
NK120(e)002:400: bzhin spyad na 'dod chen pa la'ang 'gal ba med
NK120(e)002:401: dogs bya dgos / de / mdo lam na'ang /
NK120(e)002:402: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK120(e)002:403: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK120(e)002:404: 'khor ba zhi ba'i bdag nyid la //
NK120(e)002:405: de phyir rgyal sras bsam mi khyab //
NK120(e)002:406: ces dang rdo rje gur las /
NK120(e)002:410: byang sems kyi spang bya'i gtso bo bden 'dzin gyi
NK120(e)002:411: rnam rtog yin pas lhag bsam dag par chud pa'i
NK120(e)002:412: byang chub sems dpa' la lus ngag gi las lam
NK120(e)002:413: bdun yang gnang ba bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:414: yang tshigs gsum blangs pa'i dge slong gi rgyud la
NK120(e)002:415: srog gcod kyi ltung ba gcig byung na ltung ba
NK120(e)002:416: rdzas tha dad pa gsum cig car du mi skyed
NK120(e)002:417: pa bzhin sdom pa gsum gar srog gcod pa sogs
NK120(e)002:418: bsrung bya gnad gcig pas rdzas mi 'dra ba gsum
NK120(e)002:419: tha dad du srung dgos pa dang srog gcod kyi
NK120(e)002:420: ltung ba tha dad pa gsum cig car 'byung ba
NK120(e)002:421: min kyang srog gcod pa lta bu ni so thar
NK120(e)002:422: gyi rten du rung ba'i mi bsad pa nyan thos
NK120(e)002:423: la pham pa dang srog chags gzhan bsad pa ltung
NK120(e)002:424: byed dang / byang sems kyis pha mar shes pa
NK120(e)002:425: dang sngags kyi lhar shes dgos pas nyes dmigs snga
NK120(e)002:426: ma las phyi mar shin tu je cher gyur pa
NK120(e)002:427: dang ldog cha nas gsum ga nyams pa yin pas
NK120(e)002:428: so so nas bsrung mtshams ma 'dres par bshags sdom
NK120(e)002:430: gsum ldan shi ba'i tshe yang ji srid 'tsho bar
NK120(e)002:431: zhes kun slong gi 'phen tshad kyis blangs pa'i sor
NK120(e)002:432: sdom gyi ldog cha rnams gtong yang byang sngags kyi
NK120(e)002:433: sdom pa'i ldog cha rnams ni byang chub bar du
NK120(e)002:434: zhes 'phang tshad ring ba'i phyir dang 'di'i sdom pa
NK120(e)002:435: sems las skye ba'i phyir srung sems ma nyams bar
NK120(e)002:437: dper na gsum ldan gyis theg chen gso sbyong gi dus khrims gtong len bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:438: des na ngo bo gnas 'gyur thob pa'i gsum ldan
NK120(e)002:439: gyi gang zag rten barjesa pa'i tshe sor sdom mi
NK120(e)002:440: gtong ba dang phyi mar yang bcas rkyang gi ltung
NK120(e)002:442: byis pa'i dge slong yod par khas len dgos pa sogs kyi skyon mi 'ong ngo //
NK120(e)002:443: 'thob gtong gi tshul mdo tsam ni de lags /
NK120(e)002:444: 'di dag da dung spro na zhib rgyas su zhu 'tshal /
NK120(e)002:445: sor sdom nyams pa gso rgyu yod med gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:446: spyir nyan thos rang rkang gi sor sdom la ni
NK120(e)002:447: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung ba ngo tsha khrel med
NK120(e)002:448: kyis nyams pa yin na ni tshe 'dir gso ba'i
NK120(e)002:449: skal pa med la rang rang gis 'gyod bshags chen
NK120(e)002:450: po byas na rnam smin srab pa dang ma 'ongs
NK120(e)002:451: par phan pa sogs ni los yod /
NK120(e)002:452: 'chab sems skad cig kyang ma skyes na sdom pa
NK120(e)002:453: phul te bslab pa sbyin par bshad kyang yon tan
NK120(e)002:454: khyad par can ma thob bar du gnas brtan gzhan
NK120(e)002:455: dang skal pa mi mnyam zhing mkhan po byed pa
NK120(e)002:456: sogs mchog gi spyod pa rnams spong dgos pa phyag
NK120(e)002:457: dar sogs dman spyod rnams byed dgos so //
NK120(e)002:458: da ltar rang cag lta bu'i sdom pa ni sngags
NK120(e)002:459: man chad dang 'brel yod pas sor sdom rang mtshan
NK120(e)002:460: pa nyan rang gi sdom pa lta bu ma yin
NK120(e)002:461: te / cho ga 'dul ba nyan thos lugs kyis
NK120(e)002:462: blangs pa'i sdom pa de dang po nas sam rjes
NK120(e)002:463: gang rung du gzhan phan sems bskyed kyis zin tshe
NK120(e)002:464: sdom pa de byang sems kyi nyes skyod sdom pa'i
NK120(e)002:465: tshul khrims sam theg chen sor sdom du 'gyur te
NK120(e)002:467: cho ga nyan thos lugs yin kyang /
NK120(e)002:468: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin na /
NK120(e)002:469: so sor thar pa rigs brgyad po /
NK120(e)002:470: byang sems so sor thar bar 'gyur //
NK120(e)002:471: zhes gsungs pa dang dbang thob pa dang sngags sdom du 'gyur ba yin la /
NK120(e)002:472: gang zag de la smon 'jug gnyis ka yod pas
NK120(e)002:473: byang chub sems dpa' dang dbang don gyi lta spyod
NK120(e)002:474: la mos pa brtan po yod na rig pa 'dzin
NK120(e)002:475: pa'ang yin pas ltung ba la 'chab sems yod med
NK120(e)002:476: gang yin yang gso rgyu nges par yod la /
NK120(e)002:477: theg pa che chung sems bskyed khyad zer ba de
NK120(e)002:478: bden na sems bskyed kyi zin bzhin sdom pa nyan
NK120(e)002:480: dman sems ma btang na byang sems su'ang 'gyur mi
NK120(e)002:481: rung bas gong ma thob pa dang nyams pa gsor
NK120(e)002:482: rung ba tsam re'i phan thogs gsar du 'thob rgyu
NK120(e)002:483: med na gong ma thob pa'i don yang med do
NK120(e)002:484: // gzhan yang khyim pa sngags pa sogs gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:485: spyir na dgos pa med par rten khyim pa kho
NK120(e)002:486: nas bstan 'gro'i don byed par 'dod pa ni rab
NK120(e)002:487: tu byung ba la dga' ba'i gdul bya yal bar
NK120(e)002:488: 'dor ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i lam dang shin
NK120(e)002:489: tu 'gal zhing las dang po pa'i byang sems dang
NK120(e)002:490: sngags pa la gegs che ste /
NK120(e)002:491: rab byung dang khyim pa'i yon tan dang skyon mang
NK120(e)002:492: nyung bshad pa rnams 'dir yang mi mtshungs pa'i phyir
NK120(e)002:494: de lta'i sdom brtson khyim pa yi //
NK120(e)002:495: byang sems rnams las khyad par 'phags //
NK120(e)002:497: sa thob ma gtogs khyim pa yis //
NK120(e)002:498: rgyal po'i bla ma mi bya'o //
NK120(e)002:500: sa ma thob bar khyim gyi nyes dmigs la skrag
NK120(e)002:501: ste byang chub sems dpa' rnams rten rab byung kho
NK120(e)002:502: na la smon lam 'debs pa'ang de lta bu la
NK120(e)002:504: sngon gyi dus su sangs rgyas ri rab lta bu'i
NK120(e)002:505: gsung rab la dge slong smra ba chos kyi rgyal
NK120(e)002:507: yang rgyal po dge ba'i bkod pa zhes bya ba
NK120(e)002:508: la bu stong yod pa rnams dge slong de'i mdun
NK120(e)002:510: rgyal bu tha chung snying rje cher sems zhes bya
NK120(e)002:511: ba rab tu ma byung zhing snying rje'i dbang gis
NK120(e)002:513: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa ji srid 'tsho'i bar
NK120(e)002:514: bsrung bar khas blangs pa la dge slong gis legs
NK120(e)002:515: so zhes gnang / rten khyim pa yin yang yon tan rab tu byung ba dang 'dra bar gsungs /
NK120(e)002:516: rab byung gis rgyal srid gzung bar mi 'os byang
NK120(e)002:517: chub sems dpa' rgyal srid bskyang na don che yang
NK120(e)002:518: khyim gyi nyes pa bsrung phyir gso sbyong blangs pa
NK120(e)002:519: yin no // de'i tshe dge slong de ni 'jam dpal yin la /
NK120(e)002:520: rgyal bu de ni bdag cag gi ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK120(e)002:521: bu gzhan rnams ni bskal bzang 'di'i sangs rgyas stong yin no //
NK120(e)002:522: des na yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten nges 'byung
NK120(e)002:523: gis zin pa'i so thar ris bdun las gang thub
NK120(e)002:524: tsam blangs te rang 'dod tsam ma yin par sems
NK120(e)002:525: bskyed kyis zin na sngags sdom gyi rtsa bar 'gro
NK120(e)002:526: ba yin la dbang thob pa dang thun mong gi
NK120(e)002:527: lam gyi rgyud sbyangs pa sngon song yin pas sngags
NK120(e)002:528: kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i man ngag dang 'bras
NK120(e)002:529: bu rnams kyang rgyud la smin sla ba yin te
NK120(e)002:530: sngags kyis btab pa'i lo tog nyin gcig la 'byung
NK120(e)002:531: ba bzhin no // des na phyi so thar nang
NK120(e)002:532: byang sems gsang ba sngags sdom ste phyi nang gsang
NK120(e)002:533: gsum gyi nyes pa dag cing yon tan gyi smin
NK120(e)002:534: byed dang rten brten pa'i don shin tu gal che
NK120(e)002:535: ba bzhin no // ba yin / de la dgongs
NK120(e)002:536: nas mkhas pa kha cig sdom pa gsum rten dang
NK120(e)002:537: brten par bzhed pa yin gyi /
NK120(e)002:538: rnam pa kun tu ma yin par shes dgos so //
NK120(e)002:540: phyi ru nyan thos spyod pas skyongs //
NK120(e)002:541: nang du 'dus pa'i don la dga' //
NK120(e)002:542: zhes dang o rgyan rin po ches /
NK120(e)002:543: phyi ltar lag len mdo sde'i lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)002:544: rgyu 'bras spang blang zhib pa'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)002:545: nang ltar gsang sngags thun mong lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)002:546: bskyed rdzogs don dang 'brel ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)002:547: gsang ba gsang chen a ti'i lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)002:548: tshe gcig 'od skur grol ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)002:549: ces dang tsong kha ba chen pos /
NK120(e)002:550: phyi ru nyan thos spyod pas zhi zhing dul //
NK120(e)002:551: nang du rim gnyis rnal 'byor gdengs dang ldan //
NK120(e)002:552: mdo sngags lam rnams 'gal med grogs su 'gyur //
NK120(e)002:554: 'on kyang khyim pa zhig gis thal byung du sngags
NK120(e)002:555: sdom blangs shing de rgyud ldan zhig yin na 'og
NK120(e)002:556: ma gnyis rang chog gi sgo nas ma blangs pa
NK120(e)002:557: tsam las sdom pa'i gnad rnams ni zhar la 'thob
NK120(e)002:558: ste / srog gcod spong ba sogs ni sngags la'ang
NK120(e)002:559: yod cing 'khor ba rang mtshan pa las nges par
NK120(e)002:561: nyon sgrib rang mtshan pa spong dgos pa sogs dang
NK120(e)002:562: sngags rgyud ldan yin na byang chub sems dpa' 'ang
NK120(e)002:563: yin pas khyab pa'i phyir te pha rol tu phyin
NK120(e)002:564: pa dang gsang sngags kyi theg pa gnyis ka theg
NK120(e)002:565: pa chen po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:566: so thar gyi dge slong gi tha snyad ma tshang ba tsam las don gyis gsum ldan yin la /
NK120(e)002:567: sngags kyi rtogs pa klong du gyur pa na don
NK120(e)002:568: dam pa'i dge slong mtshan nyid par 'gyur ba'ang yin
NK120(e)002:569: no // 'on kyang rab byung gi rtags cha lugs
NK120(e)002:570: 'chang mi dgos pa dang 'dul ba'i las chog rnams
NK120(e)002:571: su 'du mi dgos pa sogs dmigs bsal phran bu
NK120(e)002:572: re ma gtogs chos 'dul ba nas bshad pa'i phyi
NK120(e)002:573: dro'i kha zas tshun chad kyang nus rnyed dang dgos
NK120(e)002:574: pa med na las dang po pa'i sngags pa khyim
NK120(e)002:575: pas kyang blang dor bya dgos la /
NK120(e)002:577: rgyal ba ngas gsungs so sor thar ba yi //
NK120(e)002:578: tshul khrims rnam dag 'dul ba ma lus las //
NK120(e)002:579: sngags pa khyim pas rtags dang cho ga spang //
NK120(e)002:580: lhag ma rnams ni nyams su len par bshad //
NK120(e)002:582: gang ltar yang rtag tu dran shes dang ldan pas
NK120(e)002:583: rung mthun brtsis nas rang rgyud la nyes pa skyed
NK120(e)002:584: cing gzhan la'ang phan par mi 'gyur ba'i cha rnams
NK120(e)002:585: ni ma spangs na bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' las
NK120(e)002:586: 'das pa'i rtsa ltung ngam sbom po 'byung bas tshul
NK120(e)002:588: zhen pa che ba lta ba'i bar chad dang yengs
NK120(e)002:589: ba che ba sgom pa'i bar chad dang tshul khrims
NK120(e)002:590: 'chal ba ni spyod pa'i bar chad yin par gsungs
NK120(e)002:591: pas lta sgom kyang nyams shing dngos grub 'grub pa'i
NK120(e)002:594: zlos pa 'di la tshul khrims nyams //
NK120(e)002:595: de la grub pa thams cad med //
NK120(e)002:596: tshul khrims 'chal la thub dbang gis //
NK120(e)002:597: sngags 'grub pa ni ma gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:598: zhes sogs mang du gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:599: skye bo phal pa brgya yis do zla min //
NK120(e)002:600: zhes pa'i gang zag gi mtshan gzhi sngags pa khyim
NK120(e)002:601: pa sogs la mi go bar tshul khrims nyams pa'i
NK120(e)002:602: gang zag la gtso bor go dgos te /
NK120(e)002:603: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'di ni 'brel tshad don
NK120(e)002:604: ldan yin pas 'di la dad pa tsam skyes pa'am
NK120(e)002:605: the tshom zos sam nges shes thob bam 'brel ba
NK120(e)002:606: ci bzhag tshad dngos sam brgyud nas thar ba'i rgyur
NK120(e)002:607: mi 'gro mi srid pa'i phyir te /
NK120(e)002:608: phal pa sdom pa ma zhus pa rnams ni rang
NK120(e)002:609: bzhin gyi sdig pa kho nas dmyal bar 'gro ba
NK120(e)002:610: las thar pa'i sa bon sor byang sngags dang 'brel
NK120(e)002:611: ba med na khyi shi ba'i ro dang 'dra zhing
NK120(e)002:612: / bstan pa la zhugs nas bcas pa'i sdig pa
NK120(e)002:613: can tshul khrims 'chal ba rnams re zhig dmyal bar
NK120(e)002:614: 'gro yang 'khor ba mtha' can du byed pa'i bag
NK120(e)002:615: chags yod cing de dag la dad pa rnams lha
NK120(e)002:616: yul du skye bar bshad pas na tshul khrims 'chal
NK120(e)002:617: ba rnams ni gla ba shi ba'i ro bzhin gzhan
NK120(e)002:618: la phan pa'i rgyu yang yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:619: da ltar snyigs ma'i dus kyi rab tu byung ba
NK120(e)002:620: rnams rtags tsam du gyur kyang mu stegs pa'i drang
NK120(e)002:621: srong gi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa rnams las kyang khyad
NK120(e)002:623: sa snying 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)002:624: tsam pa ka yi me tog rgas gyur kyang //
NK120(e)002:625: me tog gzhan pa rnams las shin tu lhag /
NK120(e)002:626: dge slong tshul khrims nyams shing sdig spyod kyang //
NK120(e)002:627: mu stegs can dag thams cad kun bas mchog /
NK120(e)002:629: 'di la cho ga'i tshul khrims dang ldan yang sdom pa'i tshul khrims dang mi ldan pa zhes dang /
NK120(e)002:630: bstan pa'i chom rkun par bshad kyang ming tsam des
NK120(e)002:631: kyang gzhan zil gyis gnon nus pa sogs dper na
NK120(e)002:632: seng ge'i pags pa dang dri tsam gyis kyang ri
NK120(e)002:633: dwags rnams skrag pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:634: des na rtags tsam bzung ba la'ang phan btags na
NK120(e)002:635: bde ba chen po 'thob pa dang gnod pa byas
NK120(e)002:636: na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa
NK120(e)002:637: la gnod par byas pa dang phyogs 'dra bar 'gyur
NK120(e)002:638: ba dang / sems bskyed blangs pa'i gang zag gis
NK120(e)002:639: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i dge tshul slong la brdung bcom
NK120(e)002:640: sogs byas na rtsa ltung 'byung bar gsungs pa sogs
NK120(e)002:641: lung mang ba'i phyir dge bsnyen lcags kyi rkang pa
NK120(e)002:642: can gyis tshul khrims nyams pa'i gang zag zhig la
NK120(e)002:643: rtags 'chang ba'i gegs tsam byas pas yi dam gyi
NK120(e)002:644: zhal mthong ba'i sgrib par bshad pa'i phyir ro /
NK120(e)002:645: der ma zad sdom pa med kyang sngar rab byung
NK120(e)002:646: gi rtags blangs pa dang rtags ngur smrig gi tshal
NK120(e)002:647: bu de la gus pa tsam la'ang phan yon che
NK120(e)002:648: ste / sngon dge slong zhig nyal yod pa glang
NK120(e)002:649: chen smyos pas mthong nas snas blangs nas 'phen par
NK120(e)002:650: ste / brtsams pa na / de'i mgul na chos
NK120(e)002:651: gos kyi tshal bu thogs pa mthong bas dad pa
NK120(e)002:652: skyes te zhe sa dang bcas dal bus bzhag sogs
NK120(e)002:655: drang srong chen po'i rgyal mtshan na bza' 'dir //
NK120(e)002:656: mkhas pa thams cad shin tu bstod cing basngagasa //
NK120(e)002:657: gang zhig 'di la mchod pa byed pa rnams //
NK120(e)002:658: srid pa'i 'ching ba kun las nges par grol //
NK120(e)002:660: rab byung gi rtags cha lugs la mi gus par
NK120(e)002:661: brnyas bcos byas na dmyal ba yang sos su skyes
NK120(e)002:662: te me 'bar ba'i yo byad la spyod dgos par
NK120(e)002:663: gsungs pa'i phyir / spyir sdom pa med pa'i cha lugs 'chang ba mdo las bkag cing /
NK120(e)002:665: sems srung brtul zhugs ma gtogs pa'i //
NK120(e)002:666: brtul zhugs mang pos ci zhig bya //
NK120(e)002:668: phag mo mngon 'byung gi rgyud las /
NK120(e)002:669: de nyid sems kyi khyad par mthong gyur na //
NK120(e)002:670: brtul zhugs med kyang sangs rgyas sa la 'gro //
NK120(e)002:671: sems nyid gnyis kyi gnad dang ma bral na //
NK120(e)002:672: brtul zhugs spyad kyang sdug bsngal sna tshogs skyed //
NK120(e)002:673: ces gsungs mod kyi rtsod dus snyigs ma la bab
NK120(e)002:674: pa na rab byung rnams bu smad dang bcas shing
NK120(e)002:675: chang la spyod pa ser khyim par gyur kyang de
NK120(e)002:676: dag sangs rgyas mos pa'i dus su thar ba 'thob
NK120(e)002:677: pa snying rje pad dkar gyi mdo las gsungs pas
NK120(e)002:678: da ltar rtags tsam len pa la'ang rjes su yi
NK120(e)002:679: rangs bya dgos / sngags dang byang sems la 'brel ba'ang de las lhag par shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)002:680: dper na chos ldan gyi rgyal rigs shig ji ltar
NK120(e)002:681: dman sar lhung yang gzhan dang mi 'dra zhing gus
NK120(e)002:682: bkur bya dgos pa bzhin rjes 'jug dman pa dang
NK120(e)002:683: phal pa dman pa gnyis gtan nas mi 'dra zhing
NK120(e)002:684: tshul khrims nyams pa dang ma nyams pa'i khyad par
NK120(e)002:686: yang nyams su ma blangs pa'i chos bshad rung mi rung sogs gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:687: spyir na chos bshad dbang bskur sogs kyis gzhan don
NK120(e)002:688: byed pa la rang la rang 'dod med pa dang
NK120(e)002:689: gdul bya la mos pa yod pa zhig gal che
NK120(e)002:690: bas de ltar byung tshe mdo sde rnams lta bu
NK120(e)002:691: dang las 'bras kyi chos thun mong ba rnams ni
NK120(e)002:692: 'chad spel gyi nus pa yod pas 'chad ci thub
NK120(e)002:693: byas na dgag bya med cing phan yon shin tu
NK120(e)002:694: che ste / rin po che sna tshogs kyis rten
NK120(e)002:695: bzhengs pa dang de la mchod pa'i las brtson pa
NK120(e)002:696: ni chos mi shes pa dang khyim pa rnams la
NK120(e)002:697: che ste / gsungs la / rab tu byung ba
NK120(e)002:698: rnams ni klog spong la brtson par dkon brtsegs las
NK120(e)002:699: che ste / gsungs la / bshad cing / mdo gzhan yang /
NK120(e)002:700: gang la phan phyir nga yi chos //
NK120(e)002:701: tshul bzhin bstan pas mchod 'gyur gyi //
NK120(e)002:702: me tog byug pa mar me yis //
NK120(e)002:703: rgyal ba yang dag mchod pa yin //
NK120(e)002:705: byams pa seng ge sgra las /
NK120(e)002:706: gang g+aa'i bye snyed 'jig rten gser dag gis //
NK120(e)002:707: bkang ste gang la sbyin pa byin pa bas //
NK120(e)002:708: dus ngan tshe na tshigs bcad gcig brjod pa //
NK120(e)002:709: de yis phan 'dogs ji 'dra de la med //
NK120(e)002:710: ces sogs bshad sgrub kyi phan yon mtha' yas pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:711: sngags yin yang dbang ngam rjes gnang thob pa la
NK120(e)002:712: spyi bshad tsam re 'chad na nyes pa med cing
NK120(e)002:713: gsung pad+ma'i rigs kyi dam tshig yin pas ser snas
NK120(e)002:714: mi ston pa sogs mi rung ngo //
NK120(e)002:716: ji bzhin sgra dang dgongs min dang //
NK120(e)002:717: drang ba'i don du gang gyur dang //
NK120(e)002:718: yi ge'i don dang spyi don gyis //
NK120(e)002:719: tshogs pa la ni bshad par brjod //
NK120(e)002:720: ces mtha' drug las sgra ji bzhin pa dang dgongs
NK120(e)002:721: pa can min pa ste drang por dgongs pa dang
NK120(e)002:723: tshul bzhi las yig don dang spyi don te gnyis
NK120(e)002:724: tshogs bshad rung bar gsungs pa'ang 'di tsam nyan pa'i
NK120(e)002:725: snod rung mang ba la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK120(e)002:726: snod min log lta can yin na 'di yang 'chad mi rung ngo //
NK120(e)002:727: ji bzhin min sgra nges don dang //
NK120(e)002:728: de bzhin dgongs te bshad pa dang //
NK120(e)002:729: sbas dang mthar thug rnam pa yis //
NK120(e)002:730: slob ma la ni bshad par brjod //
NK120(e)002:731: ces mtha' drug las dang po gsum dang tshul bzhi
NK120(e)002:732: las phyi ma gnyis ni snod ldan gyi slob ma
NK120(e)002:733: sha stag la bshad dgos par gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:734: de yang snod ldan sha stag yin na ji tsam mang yang mi 'gal lo //
NK120(e)002:735: mtha' drug la tshul bzhir zhugs pa rdo rje'i theg pa kho na la yod cing /
NK120(e)002:736: ma zhugs pa ci rigs ni thun mong gi theg
NK120(e)002:737: pa yan chad la'ang yod pa yin pas spyir rgyud
NK120(e)002:738: 'chad pa lta bu de 'dra'i dbye ba dgos so
NK120(e)002:739: // gsang sngags bon du gyer ba zhes gsang rdzas
NK120(e)002:740: gsang spyod sogs tha mal gyi khrom du ston pa
NK120(e)002:741: dang 'don gyer byed pa la bya /
NK120(e)002:742: ru trar skye ba'i rgyu yin /
NK120(e)002:743: sngags khrom chos su btsong pa ni gser bye thal ba dang barje ba ltar gsungs /
NK120(e)002:744: skal min gsang sgrogs kyis lce la zhing rmo ba'i dmyal bar skye bar basha do //
NK120(e)002:745: 'on kyang chos dkon pa'i yul dang dus snyigs ma
NK120(e)002:746: bstan pa nub pa la nye ba'i dus su ni
NK120(e)002:747: blo mchog byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis 'khor ba'i
NK120(e)002:748: mtha' la bsams nas dbang bskur rgyud bshad sogs gzhan
NK120(e)002:749: don ci thub byed pa yin zhing slob ma yang
NK120(e)002:750: grangs nges med par mdzad pa yod de /
NK120(e)002:751: dper na thabs la mkhas pa'i rgyal pos mthar rgyal
NK120(e)002:752: khams mang po mnga' 'og tu sdud phyir gnas skabs
NK120(e)002:753: su sde nyung shas re dang bya ba gzhan nyams
NK120(e)002:754: shing shor ba la mi lta ba bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:755: o rgyan chen po pad+ma sam b+ha was /
NK120(e)002:756: lam gyi lam mchog gzhan don yin //
NK120(e)002:757: 'di la sgyid lugs sus byed pa //
NK120(e)002:758: de yi byang chub rgyang thag ring //
NK120(e)002:760: yang man ngag gi byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa can
NK120(e)002:761: lta bu ni rang la nyams myong gi rgyun ma
NK120(e)002:762: skyes par 'chad na sgron me lag brgyud dang bum
NK120(e)002:764: gzhan la cung zad phan yang rang rgyud stong par bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)002:766: ji ltar 'on pa rol mo mkhan //
NK120(e)002:767: gzhan dag de yis dga' byed kyang //
NK120(e)002:768: rang nyid kyis ni mi thos ltar //
NK120(e)002:769: ma bsgoms chos kyang de dang 'dra //
NK120(e)002:771: spyir na gang zag la mi rton cing chos bden
NK120(e)002:772: bzhi'i blang dor la rton pas ston pa so so
NK120(e)002:773: skye bo yin kyang gdul bya skal ldan rnam grol
NK120(e)002:774: la 'god nus pa'i lo rgyus mang po yod do
NK120(e)002:775: // rang la zhal nas snyan du brgyud pa dang
NK120(e)002:776: nyams myong gi rtogs pa'i nye brgyud dang bcas pa
NK120(e)002:777: yod na ni gdul bya mang po smin grol la
NK120(e)002:778: 'god nus pa dang rang la'ang mi gnod pa tsan
NK120(e)002:780: rang la nyams myong yod bzhin gzhan la mi ston
NK120(e)002:781: pa ni theg chen dang 'gal ba'i ltung ba yin
NK120(e)002:782: / ded dpon mkhas pas gzhan mi khrid pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:783: rang smin nas gzhan smin pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i sa lam sbyong ba yin /
NK120(e)002:784: nyan rang la de med do //
NK120(e)002:785: des na nye 'brel rnams thog mar 'dul ba nas bzung gzhan rgyud 'dul ba kho na gtso che'o //
NK120(e)002:786: nyams myong dang brgyud pa'i byin rlabs med na lung
NK120(e)002:787: khrid tsam ni gang zag mchog dman su las thob
NK120(e)002:788: kyang don 'dra / dper na gser bum dang sa bum gyi chu bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:789: chos 'chad nyan 'di yang rgyu 'bras yin pas yan lag bzhi tshang dgos te /
NK120(e)002:791: bsam pa bstan pa dang gdul bya la phan sems spro ba dang bcas /
NK120(e)002:792: sbyor ba yi ge re re nas ma chad par bgrang ba /
NK120(e)002:793: mthar thug thob blo bcas bzhi tshang dgos /
NK120(e)002:794: de'i gcig ma tshang na yan lag nyams pa'i lung
NK120(e)002:795: de gcig tu dkar ba'i las dang thar ba'i rgyur
NK120(e)002:796: mi 'gro gsungs / brgyad stong pa las /
NK120(e)002:797: kun dga' bo sher phyin 'di'i yi ge gcig kyang mi nub par khyod la gtad do //
NK120(e)002:800: tshig dang yi ge go rim bzhin ston cing //
NK120(e)002:803: de bzhin gshegs pa'am de'i nyan thos rnams las ji
NK120(e)002:804: ltar mnos pa de bzhin du chad lhag med par
NK120(e)002:805: byas shing gzhan la 'doms par byed pa ste /
NK120(e)002:807: rnam bshad rig pa las kyang gsungs /
NK120(e)002:810: shin tu legs par bklag pa dang legs par byang ba dang the tshom med par byas te'o //
NK120(e)002:812: de ltar min na sdom pa nyi shu par /
NK120(e)002:814: zhes rtsa ltung dang bstan pa 'jigs par byed pa yin no //
NK120(e)002:815: rang la nyams rtogs med par kun slong dman pas
NK120(e)002:816: chos zab mo ston na log chos su song bas
NK120(e)002:818: ded dpon blun pos bsu skyel bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:819: gzhan yang brgyud pa'ang med ji bzhin 'chad kyang mi
NK120(e)002:820: shes par zang zing gi phyir du bstan pa'i chos
NK120(e)002:821: ni gang zag mchog tu brtsi ba zhig las thob
NK120(e)002:822: kyang phan pa med cing gnod pa'ang yin te rin
NK120(e)002:823: po che'i bum pa'i chu dug tu 'gyur ba bzhin
NK120(e)002:824: dang / rnyed pa'i phyir chos 'tshong ba de'i rnyed
NK120(e)002:825: pa de log 'tsho yin pas yi dwags su skye
NK120(e)002:826: dang / bar bshad do // mdo las /
NK120(e)002:827: blun po gang zhig chos ston pa //
NK120(e)002:828: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'jig byed pas //
NK120(e)002:829: skye dgu dag ni mang po rnyed //
NK120(e)002:833: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK120(e)002:834: kyi sems can thams cad dgra bcom pa la bkod
NK120(e)002:835: pa de dag bsad pa bas tshigs su bcad pa
NK120(e)002:836: gcig ma dag par ston na nyes pa de bas
NK120(e)002:838: chos kyi ngos nas du ma dang gnod pa mi
NK120(e)002:839: srid kyang gang zag gi khams kyi chos la skyon
NK120(e)002:840: yon mchog dman du ma'i rnam par snang ba'i phyir
NK120(e)002:841: ro // brgyud ldan gyi chos tshul bzhin ston pa
NK120(e)002:842: ni gang zag phal pa ci 'dra zhig las thob
NK120(e)002:843: kyang gang zag de yang rang la phan pa che
NK120(e)002:844: bas bka' drin gyi ngos nas sangs rgyas las lhag
NK120(e)002:845: ro // pa dang / lung ni sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi phrin las dang /
NK120(e)002:846: rtogs pa ni thugs kyi phrin las yin pas lung
NK120(e)002:847: rtogs kyi chos snang ba'i gang zag de yang sku
NK120(e)002:848: gsung thugs kyi phrin las kyi rten gzugs skur blta
NK120(e)002:849: dgos so // 'adi'ang mdo'i thun mong gi lam ston
NK120(e)002:850: pa'i bla ma nyid kyis gnas skabs lha mi'i bde
NK120(e)002:851: ba dang mthar thug mchog gi 'bras bu rim gyis
NK120(e)002:852: 'grub pa'i rgyu tsam ston pa la bla ma sangs
NK120(e)002:853: rgyas su blta dgos pa las dngos yin par ma
NK120(e)002:854: dgos so // bshad la / gsang sngags kyi dbang
NK120(e)002:855: bskur rgyud 'chad pa'i bla ma ni sangs rgyas dngos
NK120(e)002:856: yin par gsungs pas de ltar blta dgos te /
NK120(e)002:857: tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha bar dor 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams ngag rang rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:859: chos smra ba ni mdor na sangs rgyas kyi mdzad
NK120(e)002:860: pa thams cad byed pa yin pas dge ba'i bshes
NK120(e)002:863: des na bshad bya'i chos kyi yan lag la brgyud pa'i srol /
NK120(e)002:866: mkhas pa'i khrid tshul rnams tshang ba gtso bor gzung dgos /
NK120(e)002:867: 'chad pa po gang zag gi go sa mtho dman
NK120(e)002:868: la ni ci yang rton pa min te bshad ma
NK120(e)002:869: thag pa ltar yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:870: don de'i zhar la 'di ltar 'ong ste phal skad kyi dpe /
NK120(e)002:871: rgyan drug rta la btags na che ba mi la thob ces pa ltar /
NK120(e)002:872: che ba chos la thob dgos na rgyan lta bu'i
NK120(e)002:873: bstod bkur dang gos de 'chad pa po la thob
NK120(e)002:874: dgos pa yin pa'i phyir na chos nyan pa po
NK120(e)002:875: de 'jig rten 'dir snang gi go sa mthon por
NK120(e)002:876: slebs pa zhig yin phyin de gtso bor bzung nas
NK120(e)002:877: / chos 'chad pa po de 'jig rten 'dir lugs
NK120(e)002:878: kyi thob tsam dma' ba yin na de la gong
NK120(e)002:879: du bkur ba dang go sa barje ba sogs mi
NK120(e)002:880: byed pa dang bzhugs gdan mtho dman tsam yang mi
NK120(e)002:881: barje ba'i gang zag des ni bla ma'i dam tshig
NK120(e)002:882: dang yang 'gal bar 'gyur bar the tshom med cing
NK120(e)002:883: / / lung rigs gnyis kar yang mi mthun te /
NK120(e)002:885: gang gis tshigs bcad gcig mnyan pa //
NK120(e)002:886: de yang bla mar ma bzung na //
NK120(e)002:887: khyi yi skye ba brgya blangs te //
NK120(e)002:888: sme sha can du skye bar 'gyur //
NK120(e)002:890: rab tu dman pa'i sa la 'dug /
NK120(e)002:892: ma gus pa la chos mi 'chad //
NK120(e)002:893: ces dang lus ngag gi gus pa med pa la sdom pa mi skye bar bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)002:894: mthon por 'dug pa la dma' bar 'dug ste chos 'chad par mi bya'o //
NK120(e)002:896: rgya gar pa'i rgyal rigs sam khyim bdag phyug po
NK120(e)002:897: ji 'dra yin yang chos nyan pa'i tshe stan ches
NK120(e)002:898: dma' ba zhig btang nas sogs mang du gsungs pa'i
NK120(e)002:899: phyir / 'chad po nyan po thams cad sdom ldan
NK120(e)002:900: yin na bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba 'byung ba'i phyir
NK120(e)002:902: rigs pa dang yang mi mthun te /
NK120(e)002:903: 'dir lugs kyi go sa tsam mtho yang de sngon
NK120(e)002:904: gyi dge 'bras dkon mchog gi drin las byung ba
NK120(e)002:905: zhig nges par yin pas chos zhu tshe chos la
NK120(e)002:906: thob dgos / chos gang zag las 'byung phyir gang
NK120(e)002:907: zag de yang 'dir snang gi go sa tsam dman
NK120(e)002:908: yang skabs der rang las go sa mthon por 'jog
NK120(e)002:910: lugs gnyis nas thams cad kyi 'og tu ma gyur
NK120(e)002:911: pa zhig yin na chos zhu dgos pa'ang min te
NK120(e)002:912: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:913: chos nyan pa po de 'phags pa dang 'chad pa
NK120(e)002:914: po so so skye bo zhig yin na ma nges
NK120(e)002:915: snyam na gang zag de 'phags par byed pa ni
NK120(e)002:916: chos kho na yin cing chos de gang zag la
NK120(e)002:917: rag las pa yin na de'i phyir yang gong ltar
NK120(e)002:918: bya dgos / dper na 'bras bu dang ljon shing bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:919: der ma zad rten khyim pa rab byung gi khyad
NK120(e)002:920: par yang mang zhing ye shes dang ldan pa gtso
NK120(e)002:921: bor 'dzin dgos par gsungs pa ni don gzhan du
NK120(e)002:923: spyir yang bstan pa'i go rim dang chos kyi che ba mi nyams pa gtso bor 'dzin dgos so //
NK120(e)002:924: des nyams myong yod med kyis chos 'chad rung mi
NK120(e)002:925: rung gang zag mchog dman las chos mchog dman du
NK120(e)002:926: 'gyur mi 'gyur sogs kyi go don rags rim tsam
NK120(e)002:927: de lags pas thugs chub zhu /
NK120(e)002:928: yang snyigs dus bslab pa phra mo bsrungs pa'i phan yon ches che tshul sogs gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:929: snyigs mas ma sbags pa'i zhing gzhan dang bstan pa
NK120(e)002:930: dar ba'i dus su tshe hril po dang bslab pa
NK120(e)002:931: rdzogs par bsrungs ba bas zhing 'di lta bu dang
NK120(e)002:932: bstan pa nub nye ba'i dus da ltar lta bu
NK120(e)002:933: la ni nyin zhag gcig gam thun tshod gcig la
NK120(e)002:934: bslab pa sna re la srung sems tsam re skyes
NK120(e)002:935: pa'i phan yon yang ches che ba'i lung ni byang
NK120(e)002:936: shar mtshams kyi sangs rgyas dbang phyug rgyal po'i zhing
NK120(e)002:937: du bskal pa'i bar tshul khrims bsrungs pa bas zhing
NK120(e)002:938: 'dir tshul khrims sna re lo zla zhag dus bsrungs
NK120(e)002:939: ba phan yon che bar mdo las gsungs pa dang
NK120(e)002:940: / ma skyes dgra'i 'gyod bsal gyi mdo las /
NK120(e)002:941: 'og gi phyogs sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi
NK120(e)002:942: bye ma snyed 'das nas 'jig rten gyi khams snang
NK120(e)002:943: ba dang ldan zhes bya ba na sangs rgyas 'od
NK120(e)002:944: zer gyi rgyal po bzhugs pa'i zhing der bskal pa
NK120(e)002:945: bcur bsam gtan la gnas shing spyod pa bas /
NK120(e)002:946: mi mjed kyi zhing 'dir snga dro gcig byams pa
NK120(e)002:947: bsgom pa bsod nams ches mang du 'phel ba dang
NK120(e)002:948: / zhing 'dir dam chos srung ba'i sems dpa' chen
NK120(e)002:949: po rnams kyis las dang nyon mongs thams cad myur
NK120(e)002:950: du byang bar gsungs pa dang gzhan yang zla ba
NK120(e)002:951: sgron me sogs mang por 'dug pa bri mi dgos
NK120(e)002:952: / la / rigs pa ni bstan pa rdzogs par
NK120(e)002:953: dar ba na gang zag rnams kyang chos kyis tshims
NK120(e)002:954: yod pa yin pas brgyags pa'i dus su zas zos
NK120(e)002:955: pa bzhin phan nus cher mi snang ba lta bu
NK120(e)002:956: / la / yin la / snyigs dus su chos
NK120(e)002:957: kyis phongs ba rnams la chos sna res kyang phan
NK120(e)002:958: pa che bar snang ba ni ltogs pa'i dus su
NK120(e)002:960: de'ang dper na me chung ngu 'bar ba la gnyen
NK120(e)002:961: po chen po bsten mi dgos shing me cher 'bar
NK120(e)002:962: ba la gnyen po chen po dang mang po bsten
NK120(e)002:963: dgos pa lta spang bya che chung dang mang nyung
NK120(e)002:964: las gnyen po yang de ltar 'gyur dgos par dgongs
NK120(e)002:965: pa dang / spang bya nyan mongs pa dar grag
NK120(e)002:966: pa'i tshe gnyen po bsrung bya sna re yang dkon
NK120(e)002:967: pa'i dus kyi nor bzhin phan pa che ba dang
NK120(e)002:968: las ka che chung dang mang nyung las las byed
NK120(e)002:969: mi mang nyung gis phan 'dogs che chung ltar /
NK120(e)002:970: sngar bstan pa dar ba'i tshe sgrub mkhan mang bas
NK120(e)002:971: bsgrub bya'i bslab pa sna res phan thogs ha cang
NK120(e)002:973: da ltar bstan pa'i bya ba ni rgya che dgos
NK120(e)002:974: kyang bstan pa'i las byed mi ni shin tu rgya
NK120(e)002:975: chung ba'i tshe bslab pa sna re bsrungs pa dang
NK120(e)002:976: chos tshig res kyang bstan pa la phan thogs che
NK120(e)002:978: lung rtogs kyi bstan pa myur du nub 'gro bas
NK120(e)002:979: de la bag chags 'jog pa sogs la dgongs nas
NK120(e)002:981: sngon bstan pa la dngos su zhugs nas bsgrub pa
NK120(e)002:982: bas da ltar mos pa tsam skyes pa'i phan yon
NK120(e)002:984: spyir bstan pa'i gnas tshad kyang du mar gsungs pa
NK120(e)002:985: rnams phal cher gdul byar skyo ba skyed phyir drang
NK120(e)002:986: don yin yang stong phrag lngar gnas par gsungs pa
NK120(e)002:987: de yang spyir thugs bskyed kyis 'phangs tshad rdzogs pa
NK120(e)002:988: dang de phan chad nyams su len pa'i sems can
NK120(e)002:989: snyigs mar gyur pas bstan pa gnas kyang sgro skur
NK120(e)002:990: dang 'gyur ba las don med pa dang /
NK120(e)002:991: bstan pa 'byung dka' zhing nub sla bar shes na
NK120(e)002:992: nges 'byung dang chos la don gnyer skye bar dgongs
NK120(e)002:993: te tshul bstan yin la nges pa'i don du ni
NK120(e)002:994: bstan pa nub pa med de /
NK120(e)002:996: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK120(e)002:997: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK120(e)002:998: sems can rnams la phan pa'i phyir //
NK120(e)002:999: bkod pa rnam pa sna tshogs ston //
NK120(e)002:1001: bskal pa mun par gyur pa na'ang theg chen 'phags
NK120(e)002:1002: pa'i 'jug po rgyun chad pa mi srid cing de
NK120(e)002:1003: dag gi thugs rgyud na bzhugs pa'i chos dkon mchog
NK120(e)002:1004: las lhag pa'i bstan pa med pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:1005: 'on kyang 'gro ba spyi'i las kyi dbang las ni nub par 'thad pa yin no //
NK120(e)002:1006: des na lnga brgya pa phrag bcu'i dbang du byas
NK120(e)002:1007: na 'bras bu'i bstan pa rdzogs la tshul khrims kyi
NK120(e)002:1008: le'u yang rdzogs zin par bshad na'ang bslab pa 'dul
NK120(e)002:1009: ba'i tshul khrims kyis mi phan zer mi rung ste
NK120(e)002:1010: / da dung lung gi bstan pa la 'dul ba'i
NK120(e)002:1011: las chog dngos su bzhugs shing de'i lag len shes
NK120(e)002:1012: pa'i mkhan slob dngos su bzhugs pa'i dus su bstan
NK120(e)002:1013: pa la las 'phro 'jog pa dang sdom pa sna
NK120(e)002:1014: re'i phan yon gong bshad ltar dang /
NK120(e)002:1015: gang zag re re'i ngos nas bzhag na da dung
NK120(e)002:1016: 'dul ba'i tshul ldan gyi dge slong sogs yod de
NK120(e)002:1018: ma 'ongs pa'i dus lnga brgya'i tha ma la dam
NK120(e)002:1019: pa'i chos rab tu rnam par 'jig par 'gyur ba
NK120(e)002:1020: na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po tshul
NK120(e)002:1021: khrims dang ldan pa yon tan dang ldan pa shes
NK120(e)002:1022: rab dang ldan pa dag 'byung ngo //
NK120(e)002:1024: yang gang zag chos la gtan mi mos shing las
NK120(e)002:1025: mtha' log pa re'i ngor ni da ltar ma zad
NK120(e)002:1026: snga nas kyang bstan pa nub tshar ba dper na
NK120(e)002:1027: mig med pa nyi ma'i ngogs la bsdad pa lta
NK120(e)002:1029: bsam pa dag pas smon lam btab pa rnams ni
NK120(e)002:1030: gang du skyes kyang chos kyi sgra thos pa mi
NK120(e)002:1031: nub ste / 'thab bral gyi lha yul na ngang
NK120(e)002:1032: pa'i rgyal po dus bzang zhes pas rtag tu lha
NK120(e)002:1033: rnams la chos ston pa yod pa sogs dpe lung
NK120(e)002:1035: nam zhig lung gi bstan pa las chog sogs kyi
NK120(e)002:1036: sgra mi snang bar gyur kyang sdig pa mi byed
NK120(e)002:1037: snyam pa re yid la 'char ba'i gang zag re
NK120(e)002:1038: yod na de'i phyogs de na da dung bstan pa
NK120(e)002:1039: yod ces smra dgos gsungs pas sems can gyi rgyud
NK120(e)002:1040: na dge sems phran bu'ang med pa'i dus su bstan
NK120(e)002:1041: pa mtha' dag nub par 'dod dgos so //
NK120(e)002:1042: de ltar na bstan pa'i lhag zhabs 'di la che zin chung zin byed dgos pa ni /
NK120(e)002:1043: dper na nyi ma nub khar sleb pa dang las
NK120(e)002:1044: byed pa rnams brel zhing rtsol ba ches cher skyed
NK120(e)002:1045: pa bzhin no // bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang /
NK120(e)002:1047: nga yi bstan pa nub khar gsal //
NK120(e)002:1050: chos nub mtha' dang ngan song 'phel ba na //
NK120(e)002:1051: mkhas pa shin tu yid dbyung bskyed byas nas //
NK120(e)002:1054: dge slong dag shes pa ni 'grib //
NK120(e)002:1057: ston pa'i bstan pa yang nges par 'jig par 'gyur na /
NK120(e)002:1058: ci'i phyir brtson 'grus dang brtul ba brtan po sgrub par mi byed /
NK120(e)002:1059: ces sogs mang du gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:1060: da lta 'bras bu mthar thug rdo rje'i theg pa
NK120(e)002:1061: dang yang gsang kun bzang thugs kyi bstan pa dar
NK120(e)002:1062: ba 'di lta bu las lam gzhan gyis nyon mongs
NK120(e)002:1063: pa gdul dka' bar gsungs pa'ang gang zag gi ngos
NK120(e)002:1065: gang zag shes rab can ni thun mong ma yin
NK120(e)002:1066: pa'i lam sgrub pa'i skal ba can yin pas zab
NK120(e)002:1067: lam la zhugs pas cho ga cing de'i rgyud na
NK120(e)002:1068: nyon mongs pa rags shing mang ba bzhin du thabs
NK120(e)002:1069: shes khyad par can sngags kyi lam yang je myur
NK120(e)002:1070: je zab tu 'gro ba yin pa'i phyir te spang
NK120(e)002:1071: bya bud shing mang na gnyen po me cher 'bar
NK120(e)002:1072: ba'i grogs su 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:1073: nyan thos pa la thar ba'i gegs su gyur pa'i
NK120(e)002:1074: 'dod yon la bag med du spyod pa'i sdig pa
NK120(e)002:1075: chen po yang byang chub kyi sems dang thabs mkhas
NK120(e)002:1076: zab mo'i lam gyis ni spang bya 'dod pa'i yon
NK120(e)002:1077: tan lngar spyod kyang dge ba chen por gyur bas
NK120(e)002:1078: gnyen po'i grogs su 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:1079: gang zhig spang bya nyon mongs che la mang yang
NK120(e)002:1080: spang bar mi spro lam du byed pa'i gnyen po
NK120(e)002:1081: bsteen nus shing byang chub 'dod pa'i dbang rnon la
NK120(e)002:1082: dgongs nas rdo rje'i theg pa gsungs te /
NK120(e)002:1084: sgo gsum dang 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug rnams
NK120(e)002:1085: rdo rje yi rang bzhin yin pa la dga' zhing
NK120(e)002:1086: rnam par rnal 'byor de la gnas /
NK120(e)002:1087: des na sangs rgyas rnams kyi thabs rdo rje'i theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)002:1089: spang bya med na gnyen po la zab pa'i khyad
NK120(e)002:1090: chos 'don rgyu med pa ni 'dul ba las kyang
NK120(e)002:1091: 'dod pa med pa'i ma ning sogs la sdom pa'i
NK120(e)002:1092: khyad par bzhag tu med par bshad pa ltar ro
NK120(e)002:1093: // lam gang yin yang spang bya'i gnyen por song
NK120(e)002:1094: na zab ces bya la gzhan du na zab pa'i
NK120(e)002:1095: // don med do // spyir yang sngags kyi theg
NK120(e)002:1096: pa na spang bya shin tu zab cing phra ba
NK120(e)002:1097: dug gsum cha mnyam mam snang gsum 'pho ba'i bag
NK120(e)002:1099: spang bya phra ba mthar thug spong ba la lam
NK120(e)002:1100: mthar thug brten dgos pa lung rigs gnyis kas grub
NK120(e)002:1101: pas sangs rgyas thams cad mthar thug sngags kyi theg
NK120(e)002:1102: par ma brten pa med par gsungs pas /
NK120(e)002:1103: sngags kyi lam zab pa yin mod sgrub pa po
NK120(e)002:1104: gang zag ma zab na bsgrub bya'i chos zab pas
NK120(e)002:1105: mi 'ong ste / dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK120(e)002:1106: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK120(e)002:1107: ces pa'ang de yin pa'i yir /
NK120(e)002:1108: dper na gser 'gyur lcags la btab ste gser du
NK120(e)002:1109: 'gyur pa'ang lcags la gser len pa'i nus pa yod
NK120(e)002:1110: pas yin gyi / gzhan shing sogs la btab pas gser mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:1111: sdig po che btsan thabs kyis grol bar bshad pa
NK120(e)002:1112: sogs kyang sbyangs 'phro'i bag chags yod pa dang dbang
NK120(e)002:1113: rab dad ldan zhig nges par dgos pa yin no
NK120(e)002:1114: // gang zag dbang rtul yin na ni 'dul ba'i
NK120(e)002:1115: rtags tsam yin la rim slob byed dgos ma gtogs
NK120(e)002:1116: sdong po bzhag ste yal gar bsnyegs pas ltung ba
NK120(e)002:1117: bzhin thams cad med par 'gyur bas sngar bshad pa
NK120(e)002:1118: // ltar bya'o // shes rab med na thabs lam
NK120(e)002:1119: 'ba' zhig gis mi grol ba ni mdo lam na'ang
NK120(e)002:1120: yod cing thabs mang ba dang thabs la mkhas pa'ang
NK120(e)002:1121: shes rab che bas yin no //
NK120(e)002:1122: des na tshe 'dir mchog gi dngos grub ma 'grub
NK120(e)002:1123: kyang dbang thob pa'i dam tshig dang yi dam gyi
NK120(e)002:1124: lha sgrub pa dang de'i bsnyen pa'ang lhag por bzlas
NK120(e)002:1125: na phan yon ches che ba dang /
NK120(e)002:1126: chos gzhan pas kyang nye lam zab mo sngags la
NK120(e)002:1127: zhugs pa'i bag chags khyad par can thob pa dang
NK120(e)002:1128: / phar phyin theg pa bas bskal pa grangs med
NK120(e)002:1129: brtson kyang thob dka' ba'ang dbang po shin tu tha
NK120(e)002:1131: dam tshig dag pa sngags bzla ba tsam las rim
NK120(e)002:1132: gnyis la 'bad pa med kyang skye ba bcu drug
NK120(e)002:1133: na mchog gi dngos grub 'grub ste /
NK120(e)002:1135: gal te ltung ba med gyur na //
NK120(e)002:1136: skye ba bcu drug dag na 'grub //
NK120(e)002:1137: ces sogs gsungs pa ni nges pa yin la /
NK120(e)002:1138: de min par 'dul bas mi phan zhes rtags tsam
NK120(e)002:1139: de yang dor nas sngags kho na la 'bad pa
NK120(e)002:1140: mang yang tshe 'dir mchog thun gyi dngos grub thob
NK120(e)002:1141: pa 'ga' la rung mod thams cad la ma nges
NK120(e)002:1142: te / sngon nyan thos kyi lam la brten nas
NK120(e)002:1143: tshe der 'bras bu thob pa de 'dra da lta
NK120(e)002:1144: sngags la zhugs pa dag la'ang dngos su mthong chos
NK120(e)002:1145: su snang ba dkon 'dug pa 'di la bltas na
NK120(e)002:1146: 'og ma spangs te sngags zab ces de gtso bor
NK120(e)002:1148: yang blo chung gang dag rang blos ma lcog pa'i
NK120(e)002:1149: lan gyis sngags kyis tshe gcig la 'tshang rgya ba
NK120(e)002:1150: dang / lus ngag yid gsum ma spangs par sku
NK120(e)002:1151: gsung thugs 'grub pa'i nye lam la the tshom za
NK120(e)002:1153: thun mong gi lam kho nas sangs rgyas 'grub cing
NK120(e)002:1154: de yang grangs med gsum sogs kyis sbyang dgos zhes
NK120(e)002:1155: 'dod pa des lam lnga sa bcu grangs med gsum
NK120(e)002:1156: sogs bgrod kyi bar tsam du sdug bsngal myong dgos
NK120(e)002:1157: pa 'phags pa srong btsan sgam pos gsungs so //
NK120(e)002:1158: lar sdom pa gsum po gcig 'gro gcig 'dug dgos
NK120(e)002:1159: rgyu rwa can dang long can lta bu zhig ni
NK120(e)002:1160: gtan nas min pas sngar bshad pa bzhin mdo sngags
NK120(e)002:1161: thams cad rang rgyud dang sbyar nas nyams su len
NK120(e)002:1162: pa la mkhas pa 'di ni shin tu gnad 'gag
NK120(e)002:1164: de dag gi gnad mdor bsdu na 'di ltar lags te /
NK120(e)002:1165: sbyang gzhi 'od gsal ba'i snying po la sbyang bya
NK120(e)002:1166: sgriib pa gsum rten sgo gsum kun slong nyon mongs
NK120(e)002:1167: gsum 'bras bu khams gsum rgyu las gsum ste de
NK120(e)002:1168: rnams sbyong byed sdom pa gsum sbyangs 'bras sku gsum
NK120(e)002:1170: sdom pa gsum po'i skabs kyi nyes spyod sdom pa dang dge chos sdud pa la /
NK120(e)002:1171: so thar gyi gzhan la gnod pa spong ba gtso bor byed /
NK120(e)002:1172: byang sems kyi gzhan gnod spong ba'i steng phan pa
NK120(e)002:1173: sgrub pa gtso bor byed pa ste lcags zangs dngul
NK120(e)002:1175: gsang sngags kyi gzhan gnod spong ba dang phan bde
NK120(e)002:1176: sgrub pa la sogs pa dngul gser du gyur pa
NK120(e)002:1177: bzhin 'og ma las zab cing rgya che la /
NK120(e)002:1178: de min gsum po gnad gcig pa las mi 'gal zhing /
NK120(e)002:1179: sdig spong dge sgrub rnams gsum po la don gyis
NK120(e)002:1180: tshang dgos pa de dag gcig tu song na ngo
NK120(e)002:1182: so thar nges 'byung gis zin pa'i sdom pa lus ngag gtso bas phyi dang /
NK120(e)002:1183: byang sems gzhan phan snying rjes zin pa'i sdom pa sems gtso bas nang dang /
NK120(e)002:1184: sngags su sems can rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sangs
NK120(e)002:1185: rgyas su bltas te glo bur gyi dri ma sbyong
NK120(e)002:1186: ba'i sems bskyed pa sogs thabs shes khyad par can
NK120(e)002:1187: dag snang gis zin pa'i rdo rje gsum gyi dam
NK120(e)002:1188: tshig sogs 'og mar ma grags pas gasnga ba zhes
NK120(e)002:1191: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing sogs gsungs pa /
NK120(e)002:1192: so thar bas bslab pa gsum la sbyar /
NK120(e)002:1193: byang sems kyi tshul khrims gsum la sbyar te byang
NK120(e)002:1194: sems kyi rang sems 'dul ba ni sems can don
NK120(e)002:1195: byed kyi mi mthun sogs rang don yid byed de
NK120(e)002:1196: 'dul zhing gzhan sems 'dul ba'ang gtso bor byed /
NK120(e)002:1197: sngags kyi bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gsum la sbyar te /
NK120(e)002:1198: sngags kyi sdig pa'i rtsa ba ma dag mtshan 'dzin
NK120(e)002:1199: sogs yin zhing dman lam skabs 'khor ba sdug bsngal
NK120(e)002:1200: dang ma dag snang zhen rang don yid byed sogs
NK120(e)002:1202: de ltar blta ba rtsa ltung yin de dag gnas 'gyur dgos so //
NK120(e)002:1203: 'jam dpal gyis dman lam skabs dge ba rang mtshan
NK120(e)002:1204: can du bltas nas bsgrub pa sogs bshags byar gsungs
NK120(e)002:1205: pa ltar ro // yang sangs rgyas kyi mtshan bzung ba sogs gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:1206: spyir sngags bzla ba'ang sangs rgyas byang sems kyi mtshan
NK120(e)002:1207: bzung ba dang lha sgom pa'ang sangs rgyas rjes su
NK120(e)002:1208: dran pa yin pas ci mang bzlas na phan yon
NK120(e)002:1210: khyad par du tshe 'dir sangs rgyas par byed pa'i thabs sgo dbang gis phyes /
NK120(e)002:1214: la spyod pas dor ba ste /
NK120(e)002:1215: sngags mtshan nyid pa'i yan lag tshang bas lha sgom
NK120(e)002:1216: sngags bzlas sogs ni tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha bar do'am
NK120(e)002:1217: ring por mi thogs par 'tshang rgya ba'i lam yin
NK120(e)002:1218: pas sgra ji bzhin par gzung dgos /
NK120(e)002:1219: gzhan yang lung dang bstun na /
NK120(e)002:1220: snyigs dus su thun mong gi theg pa bas 'bras bu mi 'grub ste /
NK120(e)002:1221: rnal 'byor ma kun tu spyod pa las /
NK120(e)002:1222: gzhan yang phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK120(e)002:1223: dus mthar dngos grub mi thob ste //
NK120(e)002:1224: chos 'di de ltar shes nas ni //
NK120(e)002:1225: bsam pa thams cad rdzogs byed yin //
NK120(e)002:1227: sngags kyi theg pas ni dus matha'i tshe der dngos grub thob ste /
NK120(e)002:1229: he ru ka dpal bzung byas na //
NK120(e)002:1231: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir da lta'i dus su sngags la 'jug pa kho na gal che'o //
NK120(e)002:1232: bskal pa rdzogs ldan dus las rim par bzlas pa'i
NK120(e)002:1233: grangs gnyis 'gyur sogs bzla bar gsungs pa ni sangs
NK120(e)002:1234: rgyas kyi gsung dang sngags kyi byin rlab nyams pa
NK120(e)002:1235: mi srid kyang gdul bya'i blo nyams shing the tshom
NK120(e)002:1236: dang las sgrib che zhing ting nge 'dzin brtan po
NK120(e)002:1238: sangs rgyas re'i mtshan bsgrags pas 'tshang rgya bar gsungs
NK120(e)002:1239: pa de 'dra dus gzhan la dgongs nas bshad pa
NK120(e)002:1240: ste skye ba brgyud nas 'tshang rgya ba'i rgyur 'gro
NK120(e)002:1241: ba'i phyir drang don yang yod /
NK120(e)002:1242: mtshan bzung ba dang thos pa tsam gyi gnas skabs
NK120(e)002:1243: kyi phan yon bshad pa rnams ni nges pa ste
NK120(e)002:1244: sangs rgyas kyi mtshan thos pas dud 'gro'i skye ba
NK120(e)002:1245: bzlog pa sogs lo rgyus mang du yod pa'i phyir
NK120(e)002:1246: ro // yang sangs rgyas bdud bzhi bcom pa la
NK120(e)002:1247: bdud kyis glags lta ba zhes sogs gsungs pa la
NK120(e)002:1248: ro // / byams pa'i stobs dang rgyal ba'i che
NK120(e)002:1249: ba ston pa'i phyir dang 'jig rten gyi che rgu
NK120(e)002:1250: dregs pa can rnams thog mar 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:1251: bdud bskul ba dang bcom pa sogs tshul bstan gyi
NK120(e)002:1252: mdzad pa sogs spyod yul bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK120(e)002:1253: yin la / sangs rgyas nyid la chos dbyings mngon
NK120(e)002:1254: du gyur pa'i phyir bdud kyi ming tsam yang mi
NK120(e)002:1255: rgyu zhing glo bur gyi bdud ni spangs zin pa'i
NK120(e)002:1256: phyir slar ldang ba mi srid de /
NK120(e)002:1257: dper na dgos pa'i dbang gis zhabs la seng ldeng
NK120(e)002:1258: gi tshal ba zug pa sogs las kyi rnam smin
NK120(e)002:1259: myong ba'i tshul ston pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:1260: 'dul mngon las sangs rgyas gang zag rang rgyud pa
NK120(e)002:1261: lam mas sbyang gi sangs rgyas su ston pa ni
NK120(e)002:1262: gdul bya'i ngor dang don yin la /
NK120(e)002:1263: theg pa chen po rnams su bskal pa grangs med
NK120(e)002:1264: sngon nas sangs rgyas par bshad cing sh+aakya thub pa
NK120(e)002:1265: sprul pa yin pas de la bdud dang las kyi
NK120(e)002:1266: rnam smin myong ba sogs mi srid do //
NK120(e)002:1267: bstan pa dang rjes 'jug la bdud kyi glags lta
NK120(e)002:1268: ba'ang bstan pa dngos ni chos kyi sku yin pas
NK120(e)002:1269: glags lta ba srid kyang glags rnyed par mi srid
NK120(e)002:1270: de bstan pa rin po che nyid seng ge shi
NK120(e)002:1271: ba'i ro bzhin gzhan gyis 'jig mi nus par bshad
NK120(e)002:1272: la / rjes 'jug gi nyams su len pa'i tshe bdud dang bdud las 'byung ba ni /
NK120(e)002:1273: rin chen chos kyang dkon la 'tshe ba'ang mang zhes
NK120(e)002:1274: pas zab mo'i chos dang 'phrad pa la bar chad
NK120(e)002:1275: mang ba de yang sems can rang rang gi bdag
NK120(e)002:1276: 'dzin las nyon gyis bskyed pa yin gyi phyi'i yul
NK120(e)002:1277: na bdud ces pa med de /
NK120(e)002:1279: 'jig rten dag na 'tshe ba gang yod dang //
NK120(e)002:1280: 'jigs dang sdug bsngal ji snyed yod pa rnams //
NK120(e)002:1281: de kun bdag tu 'dzin pa las byung na //
NK120(e)002:1282: 'dre chen des ko bdag la ci zhig bya //
NK120(e)002:1283: zhes sogs mang du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:1284: bdud la sogs pa rnams phyi na yod na ni
NK120(e)002:1285: sems can su la'ang bdud kyi glags lta ba mi
NK120(e)002:1286: srid de / sangs rgyas re res kyang khams gsum gyi bdud ma lus pa spangs zin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)002:1287: des na sems can rang rang gi bdag 'dzin las nyon ma zad par bdud kyang mi mdzad do //
NK120(e)002:1288: sems can spyi mthun gyi 'khrul gzhi bdud dga' rab
NK120(e)002:1289: dbang phyug lta bu'ang rang rang gi las snang yul
NK120(e)002:1291: sems can rnams kyis rang sems thul na bdud kyang thul ba yin te /
NK120(e)002:1293: gang gis rang gi sems 'dul na //
NK120(e)002:1295: bdud med bdud kyi las kyang med //
NK120(e)002:1296: rang gis sems kyis bcings pa bzhin //
NK120(e)002:1298: yang bcas 'gal dang srung sdom gyi nyes phan che chung sogs gsungs pa la /
NK120(e)002:1299: spyir bcas pa dang 'brel tshun chad sdom pa sna
NK120(e)002:1300: re bsrungs pa'i phan yon sngar bshad pa ltar la
NK120(e)002:1301: nyams pa'i bcas sdig gi nyes dmigs los yod /
NK120(e)002:1302: dper na zhing sa bzang po yod pa'i so nam
NK120(e)002:1303: la brtson dgos sad ser gyi gnod pa'ang bsrung dgos
NK120(e)002:1304: kyang 'bras bu longs spyod rgyun mi 'chad pa'i bde
NK120(e)002:1306: zhing med pa'i sprang po lta bu la de dag med do //
NK120(e)002:1307: de bzhin du bcas ldan gyi rab tu byung ba
NK120(e)002:1308: rnams bslab pa la 'bad cing ltung ba las bsrung
NK120(e)002:1309: dgos kyang rgyu sdom pa'i dge ba dang 'bras bu
NK120(e)002:1310: 'phral phugs kyi bde ba rgyun mi 'chad pa yod
NK120(e)002:1311: la / bcas khrims dang mi ldan pa'i khyim pa
NK120(e)002:1312: lta bu la bslab pa bsrung ba dang 'gal zla
NK120(e)002:1313: spong ba'i brtson pa mi dgos shing /
NK120(e)002:1314: nyams pa dang bsrungs pa'i nyes phan yang med do //
NK120(e)002:1315: des na sdom pa'i rtsa ba nas bsrung dgos te /
NK120(e)002:1316: sor sdom gyi rtsa ba'i pham pa gcig byung na
NK120(e)002:1317: nyis brgya lnga bcu po nyams shing srung nus med
NK120(e)002:1318: par byed pas yan lag gzhan rnams kyang nus pa
NK120(e)002:1319: chung ba dang 'gal na'ang nyams pa ltung ba la
NK120(e)002:1320: sbyor na nyes byas tsam re las mi skyed pa
NK120(e)002:1321: yin cing ltung ba de las yan lag lhag ma
NK120(e)002:1322: tsam de dag bsrungs pas skyob mi nus pas dmyal
NK120(e)002:1324: e la'i 'dab kyi lo rgyus dang sna re nyams
NK120(e)002:1325: sna re bsrungs pa'i nyes phan las bde sdug 'dres
NK120(e)002:1326: ma myong tshul gro bzhin skyes kyi gtam rgyud sogs
NK120(e)002:1327: mang du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)002:1328: byang sdom nyams na'ang dmyal bar skye ste byang sems
NK120(e)002:1329: la phrag dog gam khro ba lta bu shin tu
NK120(e)002:1330: ltung ba chen po byung na gnyen po sems bskyed
NK120(e)002:1331: dang bcas pa mthu med par byed pas na smon
NK120(e)002:1332: sems tsam re yod pas re zhig mi skyob cing
NK120(e)002:1333: 'jug sems bsrungs pa'i dge ba'i sa bon tsam re
NK120(e)002:1334: yod kyang lan grangs gzhan la smin pa'i las su
NK120(e)002:1335: 'grub pa'i phyir / byang chub kyi sems bsrung bas
NK120(e)002:1336: byang sems gzhan la skur 'debs kyi rgyu mthun myong
NK120(e)002:1337: la rnam smin dmyal ba sogs mi myong ba'i lung
NK120(e)002:1338: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // sems bskyed
NK120(e)002:1339: kyis mtshams med pa'i sdig pa sogs zil gyis gnon
NK120(e)002:1340: par gsungs pa rnams ni rang bzhin gyi sdig pa
NK120(e)002:1341: sngar yod rnams re zhig rnam smin mi 'byin cing
NK120(e)002:1342: nyes pa rim gyis srab pa la dgongs pa yin
NK120(e)002:1344: ni bcas ltung yin la bsgom pa'i stobs las byung
NK120(e)002:1345: ba'i bzod pa dang don dam sems bskyed dang zag
NK120(e)002:1346: med kyi sdom pa ma skyes bar du las kyi
NK120(e)002:1347: dbang gis ngan song du mi skye ba'i nges pa'ang
NK120(e)002:1348: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // / med
NK120(e)002:1349: de / las kyi rnam par smin pa bsam mi
NK120(e)002:1350: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // / med
NK120(e)002:1351: de / khyab // snying rje'i bdag nyid can yang
NK120(e)002:1352: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // / med
NK120(e)002:1353: de / khyab // dud 'gror skye // zhes dang
NK120(e)002:1354: sangs rgyas kyi skyes rabs rnams las 'byung ba ltar
NK120(e)002:1355: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // / med
NK120(e)002:1356: de / khyab // dud 'gror skye // yin no
NK120(e)002:1357: // 'on kyang sems bskyed btang ba'i rtsa ltung ma
NK120(e)002:1358: byung na ltung ba gzhan gyis lan rer dmyal bar
NK120(e)002:1359: 'phen byed kyis rnam smin gcig 'phangs pa de la
NK120(e)002:1360: rdzogs byed kyis tshe tshad dang sdug bsngal gyi khyad
NK120(e)002:1361: par rnams yud tsam gyis rdzogs te myong nas sems
NK120(e)002:1362: bskyed kyi stobs las myur du thar bar 'gyur ba'ang
NK120(e)002:1363: 'grub pa'i phyir / yang yod do // / med
NK120(e)002:1364: de / khyab // dud 'gror skye // yin no
NK120(e)002:1365: // yod do // sngags kyi dbang bskur thob pa'i
NK120(e)002:1366: dam sdom tshul bzhin ma byung bar nyams na lha
NK120(e)002:1367: bsgom sngags bzlas kyi phan yon mang po bshad pas
NK120(e)002:1368: mi skyob par nges par rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro
NK120(e)002:1369: ste bsrungs ba'i phan yon la zab myur gyis khyad
NK120(e)002:1370: par yod pa bzhin nyams pa'i nyes dmigs la'ang khyad
NK120(e)002:1372: khyad par du bla ma smod pa'i rtsa ltung dang
NK120(e)002:1373: bka' 'das kyi rtsa ltung byung na ni de ma
NK120(e)002:1374: bcos kyi bar du lam bsgrubs pa la 'bras bu
NK120(e)002:1375: med cing yan lag gzhan bsrungs pas kyang phan pa
NK120(e)002:1376: med de / des na sdom pa sna re tsam
NK120(e)002:1377: yod pa dang bstan pa la zhugs pa tsam byas
NK120(e)002:1378: pa'i 'bras bu ni 'khor ba'i mtha' la 'byung gi
NK120(e)002:1379: med de / / nyams pa'i 'bras bu ni 'phral
NK120(e)002:1380: du 'byung bas gnas skabs su ni phan yon las
NK120(e)002:1381: med de / / nyes dmigs che'o // yang chos
NK120(e)002:1382: la 'brel ba'i bag chags yod pa'i ngan song gi
NK120(e)002:1383: sems can rnams ni ngan 'gro gzhan dang yang mi
NK120(e)002:1384: med de / / nyes dmigs che'o // 'dra ste
NK120(e)002:1385: / o rgyan chen pos lo re bzhin du dbang
NK120(e)002:1387: lo brgya lon na dbang brgya thob pa yin //
NK120(e)002:1388: phyi mar dud 'gro skyes kyang dbang cher skye //
NK120(e)002:1389: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir dge sdig gi rgyu 'bras bslu
NK120(e)002:1390: med 'di yang shin tu yid ches pa'i gnas su
NK120(e)002:1391: blta dgos so // jo bo rje lha gcig gis /
NK120(e)002:1392: gzhan las 'bras la cung zad g.yel ba gzigs nas las 'bras la gzob /
NK120(e)002:1395: tshe phyi ma la ji ltar 'gyur zhes spyan chab 'brul lo //
NK120(e)002:1396: de'i phyir sdom pa gsum po'i bcas 'gal thams cad
NK120(e)002:1397: ji mi snyam du mi 'jog par sngar byas la
NK120(e)002:1398: 'gyod sems dang phyin chad srog la bab kyang mi
NK120(e)002:1399: byed pa'i sdom sems kyis bshags sbyangs la 'bad na
NK120(e)002:1400: ni rnam smin myong mi dgos kyang lam stegs kyi
NK120(e)002:1401: yon tan thob pa la ni shin tu 'gor bas
NK120(e)002:1402: dang po nas mi nyams pa la 'bad dgos /
NK120(e)002:1403: bshags pa la khag 'gel te ltung ba la bag
NK120(e)002:1404: med du spyod pa ni sman la khag 'gel te
NK120(e)002:1405: dug la 'dzem med du spyod pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)002:1406: mdor na bdag ni 'di ltar bsnyams te /
NK120(e)002:1407: rang bzhin gyi dge ba bar ma tsam res mtho ris su nas mtho ris skyes pa bas /
NK120(e)002:1408: sdom pa gsum zhus te nyams pas ngan song nas ngan song du 'gro bar gdams pa yin lags /
NK120(e)002:1409: der ma zad las dang las kyi rnam par smin
NK120(e)002:1410: pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab bo zhes gsungs pas
NK120(e)002:1411: 'di rigs kyi rnam bzhag mthar thug pa ni rnam
NK120(e)002:1412: mkhyen ma thob bar ji bzhin dpog mi nus la
NK120(e)002:1413: / phyogs tsam re la lung dang rigs pas da dung yang 'chad par spro /
NK120(e)002:1414: de ltar dam pa khyod kyis dri ba 'di ni
NK120(e)002:1415: bstan pa thams cad 'gal med du nyams su len
NK120(e)002:1416: cing mi lus don can du byed pa rnams la
NK120(e)002:1417: gnad 'gag chen po gcig yod par shes te /
NK120(e)002:1418: 'phral du blo la gang dran tsam bris pa de ga lags /
NK120(e)002:1419: sgra'i yi ge'i don gsungs pa 'di zur gsal zhu /
NK120(e)002:1420: zhes gangs can gyi rdo rje 'chang chen po 'jam
NK120(e)002:1421: dbyangs mkhyen brtse dbang po'i drung yig mkhas pa tshe
NK120(e)002:1422: ring bkra shis kyis dgongs bzhed dris lan du mang
NK120(e)002:1423: du thos kyang don la blun po'i mtshan gzhi can
NK120(e)002:1424: mkhas pa'i sgro btags pa rme ri dge slong bsod
NK120(e)002:1425: nams chos 'grub kyis dpal spungs yang khrod nas bris
NK120(e)002:1426: pa 'di kun gyi thugs nyams su 'thad par gyur
